B%20for%20a%20coalition%20stemming%20from%20broad%20public%20support%20for%20issues%20like%20universal%20background%20checks%20for%20gun%20purchases%20and%20tackling%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Congress%2C%2010%20Republicans%20broke%20with%20their%20party%20to%20impeach%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20after%20January%206.%20Eight%20of%20them%20were%20defeated%20by%20Trump-backed%20primary%20challengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%2C%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20the%20attack%20ads%20that%20a%20primary%20challenger%20could%20run%20against%20a%20Republican%20who%20chose%20to%20back%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20career%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDemocrats%20prop%20up%20a%20Republican%20speaker%20in%20exchange%20for%20concessions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20idea%20was%20initially%20posed%20to%20me%20by%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Greg%20Casar%2C%20a%20top%20leader%20in%20the%20Congressional%20Progressive%20Caucus.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-motion-vacate-progressive-democrats-support-kevin-mccarthy-2023-9%5C%22%3Efloated%20a%20scenario%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20Democrats%2C%20or%20at%20least%20progressives%2C%20secure%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkatherine-clark-kevin-mccarthy-motion-vacate-biden-impeachment-2023-9%5C%22%3Esome%20sort%20of%20commitment%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20McCarthy%20in%20exchange%20for%20tanking%20Gaetz's%20motion%20to%20vacate.%20Casar%20comes%20from%20Texas%2C%20where%20Democrats%20are%20still%20allowed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.texastribune.org%2F2023%2F02%2F08%2Ftexas-legislature-democrats-chair-committees%2F%5C%22%3Ehold%20some%20chairmanships%20in%20the%20state%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20minority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Texas%20example%20is%20that%20sometimes%20you%20vote%20for%20a%20Republican%20speaker%2C%20but%20then%20you%20get%20a%20third%20of%20the%20chairs%2C%26quot%3B%20Casar%20told%20me%20on%20T