0world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECh%C3%A2teau%20de%20Tr%C3%A9cesson%20%E2%80%94%20Brittany%2C%20France%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Castle%20of%20Trecesson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5db88687dee0192ee21b7ad2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222325%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ch%C3%A2teau%20de%20Tr%C3%A9cesson.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Gerard%20SIOEN%2FGamma-Rapho%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ch%C3%A2teau%20de%20Tr%C3%A9cesson%20is%20said%20to%20be%20haunted%20by%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20buried%20alive%20on%20the%20property%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelocal.fr%2F20181031%2Fseven-ghost-stories-from-frances-most-haunted-castles%5C%22%3EThe%20Local%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legend%20goes%20that%20a%20thief%20had%20been%20lurking%20around%20the%20Ch%C3%A2teau%20de%20Tr%C3%A9cesson%20and%20spotted%20two%20people%20digging%20a%20hole.%20Then%2C%20the%20two%20people%20dragged%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20bridal%20gown%2C%20and%20threw%20her%20body%20into%20the%20hole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thief%20ran%20home%20and%20told%20his%20wife%20about%20what%20he'd%20seen%2C%20claiming%20that%20he'd%20overheard%20the%20two%20people%20saying%20they'd%20buried%20the%20young%20woman%20alive%20because%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bdishonored%26quot%3B%20her%20family.%20His%20wife%20told%20him%20to%20run%20back%20and%20save%20the%20young%20woman%2C%20but%20once%20he%20returned%2C%20the%20young%20bride%20was%20already%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMorgan%20House%20%E2%80%94%20Kalimpong%2C%20India%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223043%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Morgan%20House%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dbb036fdee01974f3021135%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222282%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorgan%20House.%3Cp%3EDIPTENDU%20DUTTA%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C