%20figures%2C%20and%20even%20hearing%20disembodied%20voices%20around%20the%20property%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toronto.com%2Fnews%2Fghost-stories-abound-at-casa-loma%2Farticle_fc61603d-e468-5ff5-a3a1-4a73bb7ae462.html%3F%5C%22%3EToronto.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20castle%20is%20said%20to%20be%20haunted%20by%20several%20ghosts%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20White%20Lady%26quot%3B%3B%20she%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20a%20maid%20on%20the%20property%20in%20the%20early%201900s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20are%20the%20tunnels%20underneath%20the%20property%2C%20in%20which%20guests%20have%20reported%20speaking%20to%20and%20otherwise%20interacting%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eanother%3C%2Fem%3E%20ghost.%20Reports%20say%20it's%20the%20ghost%20of%20a%20friend%20of%20Sir%20Henry%2C%20who%20was%20hired%20to%20look%20after%20his%20horses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20rumored%20sightings%20of%20the%20Pellatts%20themselves.%20People%20say%20they've%20spotted%20Henry%20glaring%20out%20of%20the%20windows%20on%20the%20second%20floor%2C%20and%20Mary%2C%20who%20has%20been%20noted%20for%20turning%20off%20the%20cameras%20of%20those%20who%20have%20tried%20to%20capture%20a%20snapshot%20of%20her%20in%20the%20afterlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKellie's%20Castle%20%E2%80%94%20Batu%20Gajah%2C%20Malaysia%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224453%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kellies%20Castle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dbb048ddee01977a3389223%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKellie's%20Castle.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Education%20Images%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKellie's%20Castle%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20haunted%20places%20in%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20of%20Kellie's%20Castle%20began%20in%201915%20but%20ceased%20in%201926%20after%20its%20owner%2C%20William%20Kellie%20Smith%2C%20died.%20Soon%20after%2C%20the%20castle%20was%20sold%20off%20and%20fell%20into%20a%20state%20of%20disrepair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%2C%20his%20spirit%20is%20said%20to%20haunt%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20castle%2C%20and%20a%20young%20girl%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20his%20daughter%2C%20has%20also%20supposedly%20been%20seen%20around%20the%20property%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Ipoh%20Tourism%20Board's%20official%20website.%20During%20WWII%2C%20Japanese%20soldiers%20were%20said%20to%20have%20executed%20prisoners%20on%20the%20castle%20grounds%2C%20leaving%20an%20eerie%2C%20unsettling%20vibe%20as%20one%20enters%20the%20property.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECharleville%20Castle%20%E2%80%94%20County%20Offaly%2C%20Ireland%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charleville%20Castle%20in%20Ireland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dbb073fdee01971dc7ef617%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharleville%20Castle.%3Cp%3EBy%20Dontsu%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECharleville%20Castle%20dates%20back%20to%201798%20when%20it%20was%20built%20for%20Earl%20of%20Charleville%20William%20Bury%20and%20his%20family.%20It%20remained%20in%20the%20family%20until%201963%20when%20ancestor%20Charles%20Bury%20died%20suddenly%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishcentral.com%2Ftravel%2Ftravel-tips%2Fhaunted-places-ireland-visit-halloween%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIrish%20Central%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20people%20report%20hearing%20disembodied%20voices%20and%20classical%20music%20throughout%20the%20property.%20Visitors%20have%20claimed%20that%20sounds%20of%20children%20playing%20fill%20the%20air%20in%20the%20room%20that%20was%20once%20a%20nursery%2C%20and%20the%20apparition%20of%20a%20young%20girl%20named%20Harriet%20has%20been%20