20an%20October%202020%20presidential%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20lawsuit%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Merrimack%20Superior%20Court%20in%20the%20state%20of%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20Giuliani's%20lawyers%20contend%20that%20Biden%20defamed%20Giuliani%20twice%20during%20a%20televised%20debate%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20October%2022%2C%202020%2C%20when%20Biden%20was%20a%20candidate%20seeking%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20at%20two%20points%20during%20the%20debate%2C%20Biden%20falsely%20accused%20Giuliani%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3BRussian%20pawn%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20dismissed%20Giuliani's%20criticisms%20of%20his%20son%20Hunter's%20laptop%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20ex-mayor%20believed%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunch%20of%20garbage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefendant%20Biden%20knew%20that%20the%20preceding%20statement%20about%20the%20laptop%20and%20asserting%20that%20the%20Plaintiff%20lied%20about%20the%20content%20of%20the%20laptop%20were%20untrue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20contends%2C%20while%20also%20charging%20that%20now-Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20had%20sought%20to%20discredit%20Giuliani%20regarding%20Hunter%20Biden's%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20argues%20that%20Biden's%20comments%20have%20damaged%20Giuliani's%20reputation%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20do%20so%2C%20preventing%20him%20from%20holding%20%26quot%3Bpositions%20that%20require%20credibility%2C%20trust%2C%20decision-making%2C%20and%20independence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani's%20attorneys%20then%20proceeded%20to%20list%20Giuliani's%20career%20accomplishments%20as%20proof%20of%20his%20positive%20reputation%2C%20referencing%20his%20%26quot%3Bsterling%20and%20unimpeachable%20character.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20over%20fifty%20years%2C%20the%20Plaintiff%20has%20provided%20public%20and%20professional%20service%20for%20and%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20American%20people%20that%20only%20can%20be%20regarded%20as%20historic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20went%20on%20to%20detail%20his%20decadeslong%20legal%20career%2C%20notably%20his%20stint%20as%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20where%20he%20prosecuted%20some%20of%20the%20highest-profile%20cases%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20also%20pointed%20to%20his%20two%20terms%20as%20New%20York%20City's%20mayor%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20has%20also%20been%20called%20%26quot%3BAmerica's%20Mayor%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20label%20that%20some%20assigned%20to%20him%20after%20his%20response%20to%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20September%2011%2C%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20Giuliani's%20public%20actions%20and%20statements%20have%20been%20closely%20tethered%20to%20the%20political%20fortunes%20of%20Trump%2C%20who%20lost%20the%202020%20election%20to%20Biden%20and%20has%20baselessly%20claimed%20since%20that%20he%20was%20the%20true%20victor%20of%20the%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20and%20weeks%20after%20the%202020%20election%2C%20Giuliani%20%E2%80%94%20who%20at%20the%20time%20was%20Trump's%20personal%20attorney%20%E2%80%94%20traveled%20to%20key%20swing%20states%20that%20included%20Arizona%20and%20Georgia%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20pressure%20GOP%20governors%20and%20lawmakers%20to%20overturn%20Biden's%20respective%20victories%20in%20those%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Giuliani%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiuliani-lawyers-lawsuit-1-million-unpaid-legal-fees-2023-9%5C%22%3Esued%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20his%20former%20attorney%20for%20nearly%20%241.4%20million%20over%20what%20he%20said%20was%20money%20owed%20after%20defending%20the%20former%20mayor%20in%20election%20interference%20probes%20connected%20to%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20real%20shame%20when%20lawyers%20do%20things%20like%20this%2C%20and%20all%20I