20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd6i58v0o_thangjing-hill_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThangting%20(or%20Thangjing)%20hill%20and%20Moirang%20town%20(in%20red%20circle)%2C%20near%20Loktak%20Lake%20in%20Manipur.%20Click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fsdlt0s9_thangjing-hill_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20high%20resolution%20pic%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20civil%20society%20groups%20including%20the%20Association%20of%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20Americas%20(AMA)%20have%2C%20however%2C%20requested%20the%20government%20to%20clear%20the%20alleged%20encroachment%20from%20Thangjing%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20make%20a%20comparison%20on%20why%20this%20is%20an%20extremely%20serious%20matter%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20desecration%20of%20Thangjing%20hill%20would%20be%20the%20same%20as%20the%20desecration%20of%20Bharat's%20holy%20sites%20in%20the%20mountains%20like%20Kedarnath%2C%20Badrinath%2C%20or%20the%20Amarnath%20shrine%2C%26quot%3B%20AMA%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20hill%20range%20lies%20between%20Moirang%20and%20Churachandpur%20districts%2C%2040%20km%20apart.%20Churachandpur%20is%20where%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20began%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20in%20Moirang%20under%20Bishnupur%20district%20-%20home%20to%20the%20northeast's%20largest%20freshwater%20lake%20Loktak%20-%20consider%20the%20deity%20Ibudhou%20Thangjing%20the%20area's%20guardian.%20Photos%20taken%20with%20powerful%20zoom%20lenses%20and%20drone%20footage%20show%20the%20objects%20on%20the%20hill%2C%20giving%20it%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20place%20that%20has%20been%20desecrated%2C%20Moirang%20MLA%20Thongam%20Shanti%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Shanti%20alleged%20the%20cross%20and%20the%20flag%20came%20up%20on%20the%20same%20spot%20where%20the%20shrine%20of%20Ibudhou%20Thangjing%20stands%2C%20though%20Mr%20Vualzong%20denied%20any%20such%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20terrorists%20do%2C%20encroaching%20upon%20other%20people's%20sacred%20land.%20We%20grew%20up%20living%20in%20harmony%20with%20other%20communities%20and%20yes%2C%20we%20have%20been%20living%20peacefully%20with%20the%20tribes%20too.%20Only%20in%20recent%20times%20a%20lot%20of%20infiltration%20has%20taken%20place%20from%20Myanmar.%20These%20people%20don't%20know%20the%20land%2C%20don't%20respect%20the%20land.%20They%20want%20to%20break%20up%20Manipur.%20The%20tribes%20we%20have%20been%20living%20with%20wouldn't%20desecrate%20our%20holiest%20shrine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLA%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Vualzong%20said%20the%20allegations%20by%20Moirang%20residents%20that%20a%20flag%20of%20an%20insurgent%20group%20has%20been%20installed%20atop%20Thangjing%20hill%20is%20a%20blatant%20lie.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20for%20the%20flag%2C%20it%20is%20not%20the%20ZRA%20flag%2C%20but%20a%20Zomi%20or%20a%20community%20flag%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Thangting%20(Thangjing)%20hill%2C%20Churachandpur%20(bottom%20red%20circle)%20and%20Moirang%20(upper%20red%20circle)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Thangting%20(Thangjing)%20hill%2C%20Churachandpur%20(bottom%20red%20circle)%20and%20Moirang%20(upper%20red%20circle)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fbjv825mo_thangjing-hill_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThangting%20(Thangjing)%20hill%2C%20Churachandpur%20(bottom%20red%20circle)%20and%20Moirang%20(upper%20red%20circle).%20Click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fjvkka2h8_thangjing_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20high%20resolution%20pic%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20cabinet%20in%20October%20last%20year%20took%20a%20decision%20to%20include%20four%20hectares%20of%20Ibudhou%20Thangjing%2C%20two%20hectares%20of%20Koubru%20Laipham%20and%20four%20hectares%20of%20Lai%20Pukhri%20under%20Section%204%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Ancient%20and%20Historical%20Monuments%20and%20Archaeological%20Sites%20and%20Remains%20Act%2C%201976%2C%20which%20protects%20these%20places%20from%20encroachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Moirang%20committee%20on%20protecting%20the%20Koubru%20and%20Thangjing%20ranges%20has%20filed%20a%20first%20information%20report%20over%20the%20alleged%20encroachment.%20The%20committee%20alleged%20the%20Kuki%20Students'%20Organisation%20in%20May%20last%20year%20told%20Moirang%20residents%20to%20take%20their%20permission%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20offer%20prayers%20at%20the%20hilltop%20shrine.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20tension%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIbudhou%20Thangjing's%20shrine%20on%20the%20hill%20was%20not%20visible%20from%20Moirang%20valley%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20is%20visible%20now%20with%20binoculars%20since%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20hillside%20has%20been%20deforested%2C%20a%20Moirang%20resident%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20lakeside%20town%20and%20who%20has%20done%20studies%20on%20deforestation%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20communities%20had%20been%20living%20peacefully%20until%20the%20Thangjing%20hill%20subdivision%20was%20renamed%20to%20Thangting%2C%20a%20name%20recognised%20by%20the%20hill%20tribes.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20created%20the%20ground%20for%20confrontation%20over%20Thangjing%20hill.%20Even%20then%2C%20through%20negotiation%2C%20the%20Ibudhou%20Thangjing%20committee%20went%20to%20the%20hill%20shrine%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Moirang%20resident%20said%2C%20adding%20deforestation%20is%20clearly%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20to%20cross%20a%20few%20initial%20lower-height%20ranges%2C%20then%20a%20middle%20spot%20before%20finally%20reaching%20the%20hilltop%20shrine.%20After%20the%20government%20built%20a%20road%20from%20Kwakta%20side%20to%20the%20hilltop%2C%20insurgents%20began%20misusing%20the%20road%20to%20travel%20up%20and%20down%20fast%2C%20the%20Moirang%20resident%20alleged.%20Earlier%2C%20only%20a%20dirt%20path%20existed%20till%20the%20hilltop.%20Kwakta%20saw%20major%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20past%20months%3B%20it%20lies%20between%20Moirang%20and%20Thangjing%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThangjing%20hill%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20abode%20of%20the%20Ibudhou%20Thangjing%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20revered%20deities%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Moirang%20clan%20in%20particular%20for%20over%202%2C000%20years.%20The%20legend%20of%20Khamba%20and%20Thoibi%20and%20the%20ancient%20Moirang%20principality%20are%20inseparably%20linked%20to%20this%20ancient%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieutenant%20General%20Konsam%20Himalay%20Singh%2C%20PVSM%2C%20UYSM%2C%20AVSM%20YSM%20(retired)%20-%20the%20first%20officer%20from%20the%20northeast%20to%20become%20a%20Lieutenant%20General%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20-%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20in%20Hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20this%20sacred%20site%20was%20included%20in%20the%20newly%20created%20hill%20district%20of%20Churachandpur%20in%201969.%20This%20sacred%20site%20became%20a%20friction%20point%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20when%20contested%20rights%20and%20claims%20hardened%20over%20the%20site%20between%20a%20few%20hill%20villages%20and%20the%20believers%20of%20the%20deity.%20I%20am%20sanguine%20that%20the%20parties%20involved%20will%20respect%20the%20faith%20of%20over%20a%20million%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Lt%20General%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaheshwar%20Thounaojam%2C%20a%20Manipur%20resident%20and%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(Athawale)%2C%20said%20Thangjing%20hill%20is%20a%20cultural%20heritage%20site%20for%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIbudhou%20Thangjing%20is%20a%20primordial%20deity%20of%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20for%20which%20we%20celebrate%20the%20first%20Sunday%20of%20the%20Meitei%20New%20Year%20or%20Cheiraoba.%20I%20and%20every%20Meitei%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20hoisting%20of%20the%20ZRA%20flag%20at%20our%20cultural%20heritage%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thounaojam%20told%20NDTV%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20insurgent%20group%20Zomi%20Revolutionary%20Army's%20flag%2C%20which%20the%20ITLF%20spokesperson%20Mr%20Vualzong%20has%20already%20denied%20is%20not%20the%20insurgent%20group's%20flag%20but%20of%20a%20community%2C%20indicating%20the%20linking%20of%20the%20flag%20with%20the%20insurgent%20group%20is%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696448640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvdl3rts_thangjing-hill_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-cross-and-flag-atop-manipurs-sacred-thangjing-hill-in-moirang-police-case-filed-4450944%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20appearance%20of%20a%20cross%20and%20a%20community%20flag%20atop%20a%20hill%20near%20Manipur's%20Moirang%20district%20has%20raised%20a%20massive%20controversy%2C%20as%20the%20hill%20has%20a%20sacred%20site%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20this%20lakeside%20district%2C%2060%20km%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-cross-and-flag-atop-manipurs-sacred-thangjing-hill-in-moirang-police-case-filed-4450944%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-cross-and-flag-atop-manipurs-sacred-thangjing-hill-in-moirang-police-case-filed-4450944%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-cross-and-flag-atop-manipurs-sacred-thangjing-hill-in-moirang-police-case-filed-4450944%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2241%25%20of%20amphibian%20species%20worldwide