%20reported%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElectric-car%20giant%20BYD%20first%20launched%20as%20a%20battery%20maker%20but%20has%20since%20grown%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-automakers-market-share-competing-tesla-global-expansion-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earguably%20the%20most%20impressive%20and%20quick-moving%20EV%20manufacturer%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20Chuanfu%20founded%20BYD%20in%201995%2C%20and%20alongside%20business%20partner%20Stella%20Li%2C%20the%20company%20is%20now%20on%20track%20to%20potentially%20best%20Tesla%20as%20the%20world's%20top%20seller%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%20It%20sold%20more%20than%20431%2C000%20EVs%20in%20Q3%2C%20putting%20it%20second%20to%20Tesla's%20435%2C000%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20but%20both%20companies%20are%20targeting%201.8%20million%20EV%20sales%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Sokol%2C%20at%20the%20time%20a%20lieutenant%20of%20Warren%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20noticed%20BYD's%20momentum%20and%20visited%20the%20company%20in%20Shenzhen%20as%20early%20as%202008%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos%2Fhow-chinas-byd-became-teslas-biggest-threat-5edfd080%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20the%20two%20BYD%20executives%20told%20Sokol%20about%20the%20company's%20competitive%20advantages%2C%20eventual%20global%20expansion%20plans%2C%20and%20clean%20battery%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20then%20took%20a%20sip%20from%20a%20glass%20of%20BYD's%20battery%20fluid%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20told%20the%20paper%2C%20as%20a%20way%20to%20show%20his%20confidence%20in%20how%20green%20its%20in-house%20tech%20was%20to%20the%20former%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20exec.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Berkshire%20bought%20a%2010%25%20stake%20in%20BYD%20for%20%24232%20million.%20That%20investment%20catapulted%20