ave%20in%20Mumbai%20about%20the%20timeline%20of%20his%20attempt%20to%20form%20a%20short-lived%20government%20with%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20political%20surprises%20in%20Maharashtra%20after%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20the%20then%20Governor%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Koshyari%20swore%20in%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20as%20deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20November%2023%2C%202019.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20fell%20after%20about%2072%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPost%20assembly%20elections%20in%202019%2C%20we%20were%20discussing%20government%20formation%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20We%20had%20even%20finalised%20portfolio%20distribution%20and%20guardian%20ministers'%20responsibilities.%20But%20Pawar%20made%20a%20U-turn%20and%20backed%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20insisting%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20impose%20the%20President's%20Rule%20in%20the%20state%20was%20taken%20with%20Mr%20Pawar's%20consent.%20NCP%20had%20won%2054%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20results%20of%20which%20were%20announced%20on%20October%2024%2C%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20105%20of%20the%20288%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20was%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20won%2056%20seats.%20However%2C%20the%20allies%20parted%20ways%20after%20bickering%20over%20power-sharing%2C%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20being%20the%20bone%20of%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20deadlock%2C%20the%20President's%20Rule%20was%20imposed%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20has%20to%20ask%20every%20political%20party%20whether%20it%20would%20like%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20The%20NCP%20refused%20to%20do%20so%20and%20its%20letter%20(to%20this%20effect)%20was%20typed%20at%20my%20residence%20in%20Mumbai.%20Pawar%20suggested%20some%20corrections%2C%20which%20were%20made%2C%20and%20then%20it%20(letter)%20was%20submitted%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20claiming%20that%20Pawar's%20consent%20had%20been%20taken%20before%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20the%20President's%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPawar%20told%20us%20that%20he%20could%20not%20take%20a%20decision%20to%20tie%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20short%20period.%20Pawar%20said%20he%20would%20first%20tour%20the%20state%20and%20announce%20his%20decision%20to%20form%20a%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%20after%20convincing%20people.%20Pawar%20said%20he%20would%20need%20one%20month%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Sharad%20Pawar%20made%20a%20U-turn%20about%20forming%20the%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20his%20nephew%20and%20NCP%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20tried%20to%20form%20the%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20announced%20that%20the%20then%20Shiv%20Sena%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20had%20been%20unanimously%20chosen%20to%20head%20an%20alliance%20of%20Sena%2C%20NCP%20and%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20formed%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MVA%20government%20fell%20last%20year%20after%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20along%20with%2039%20Sena%20MLAs%2C%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20with%20Fadnavis%20as%20his%20deputy%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20broke%20away%20from%20NCP%20in%20July%20this%20year%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20same%20event%20later%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20rejected%20Mr%20Fadnavis's%20claim%20about%20his%20%E2%80%9CU-turn%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20president%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20the%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20decide%20to%20impose%20the%20President's%20Rule%2C%20why%20should%20we%20say%20no%3F%20They%20have%20the%20numbers%2C%20why%20would%20they%20listen%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETerming%20Mr%20Fadnavis's%20claims%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%2C%20NCP's%20chief%20spokesperson%20Mahesh%20Tapase%20said%20their%20party%20under%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20consistently%20upheld%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20remind%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20impose%20the%20President's%20Rule%20in%20Maharashtra%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20and%20any%20insinuation%20that%20it%20was%20influenced%20by%20Pawar%20is%20false%20and%20misleading%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20NCP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETapase%20said%20their%20party%20is%20committed%20to%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20statements%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20purposely%20made%20to%20confuse%20the%20electorate%20who%20stands%20with%20%E2%80%9CSharad%20Pawar%20saheb%E2%80%9D%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20%E2%80%9COperation%20Lotus%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20substantially%20damage%20the%20NCP's%20%26quot%3Bvote%20share%26quot%3B%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20hence%20repeated%20attempts%20are%20being%20made%20by%20Fadnavis%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconfuse%20the%20electorate%E2%80%9D%2C%20Tapase%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wonder%20why%20the%20BJP%20cannot%20get%20over%20its%20obsession%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20NCP%20leader%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20can%20never%20forget%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cincompetent%E2%80%9D%20government%20of%20Fadnavis%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20infants%20and%20others%20in%20Nanded%20and%20Aurangabad%2C%20now%20renamed%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20targeted%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20in%20Maharashtra%20over%20recent%20deaths%20in%20state-run%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2031%20deaths%20were%20recorded%20at%20the%20Dr%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Government%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Nanded%20in%2048%20hours%20since%20September%2030%2C%20while%2018%20patients%20died%20at%20the%20Government%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20within%2024%20hours%20ending%20at%208%20am%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696446420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F5uaoivt_devendra-fadnavis_625x300_30_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-vs-d-fadnavis-over-president-rule-in-maharashtra-in-2019-4450083%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20President's%20Rule%20was%20imposed%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%202019%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20NCP%20president%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20said%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20NCP%20chief%20rejected%20the%20claim%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20call%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-vs-d-fadnavis-over-president-rule-in-maharashtra-in-2019-4450083%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-vs-d-fadnavis-over-president-rule-in-maharashtra-in-2019-4450083%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-vs-d-fadnavis-over-president-rule-in-maharashtra-in-2019-4450083%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Hunting%20Wives%E2%80%99%20Series%20Ordered%20at%20Starz%2C%20Rebecca%