r%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20said%20all%20those%20who%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20survey%20data%20should%20ask%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20get%20it%20conducted%20for%20the%20entire%20country.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20have%20its%20cake%20and%20eat%20it%20too%2C%20by%20both%20welcoming%20and%20criticising%20the%20survey%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20said%20that%20while%20his%20party%20had%20supported%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar%2C%20no%20enumerator%20had%20met%20him%20or%20his%20family%20to%20gather%20their%20information%20despite%20him%20being%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Patna%20Sahib.%20He%20said%20someone%20had%20asked%20a%20person%20outside%20their%20house%20for%20the%20details%20and%20alleged%20that%20similar%20complaints%20had%20been%20received%20from%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20repeated%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20charge%20that%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20Congress%20and%20three%20Left%20parties%2C%20had%20got%20the%20survey%20done%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20data%20be%20made%20public%20to%20ensure%20transparency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20public%20relations%20department%20issued%20a%20rebuttal%20and%20said%20that%20the%20information%20from%20the%20MP%20was%20collected%20as%20per%20the%20laid-down%20norms%20and%20that%20the%20data%20could%20not%20be%20released%20as%20that%20would%20lead%20to%20privacy%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEscalation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Prasad%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20the%20signature%20of%20the%20house%20owner%20is%20a%20must%20as%20per%20the%20caste%20survey%20form%2C%20and%20his%20was%20not%20taken.%20He%20alleged%20that%20lakhs%20of%20people%20have%20similar%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20importance%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Public%20Relations%20Department%3F%20My%20direct%20question%20is%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20caste%20survey%20form%2C%20the%20signature%20of%20the%20house%20owner%20is%20necessary%20but%20my%20signature%20has%20not%20been%20taken%20nor%20have%20I%20been%20contacted%20even%20though%20I%20am%20the%20head%20of%20the%20family.%20Lakhs%20of%20people%20in%20Bihar%20have%20similar%20concerns%20that%20they%20were%20not%20contacted%20by%20the%20surveyors%20and%20their%20signatures%20were%20not%20taken.%20Misrepresentation%20should%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Prasad%20posted%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Mr%20Prasad's%20comments%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20parties%20in%20Bihar%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%2C%20had%20supported%20the%20caste%20survey.%20He%20also%20slammed%20the%20party%20for%20both%20welcoming%20the%20survey%20and%20criticising%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20caste%20survey%20has%20been%20done%20and%20now%20some%20people%20are%20raising%20objections.%20They%20are%20welcoming%20the%20survey%20and%20objecting%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20If%20they%20have%20so%20many%20objections%2C%20why%20don't%20they%20ask%20PM%20Modi%20to%20get%20the%20Centre%20to%20do%20it%3F%20How%20long%20have%20we%20been%20making%20that%20demand%3F%20If%20they%20don't%20trust%20our%20survey%2C%20they%20should%20ask%20Modiji%20to%20get%20it%20done%20in%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20and%2C%20if%20not%2C%20at%20least%20in%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20they%20have%20to%20do%20is%20add%20a%20column.%20Forget%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20conduct%20the%20normal%20Census%20since%202021.%20These%20people%20raise%20objections%20when%20someone%20gets%20the%20wo