uted%20Territory%20Narrative%20For%20Kashmir%26quot%3B%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENewsClick%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20case%20filed%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20following%20allegations%20that%20the%20portal%20received%20money%20for%20pro-China%20propaganda%2C%20allegedly%20conspired%20to%20peddle%20a%20narrative%20that%20Kashmir%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20are%20disputed%20territories%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Purkayastha%20and%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%20were%20arrested%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20remand%20application%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSecret%20inputs%20revealed%20that%20Purkayastha%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20and%20some%20other%20Chinese%20employees%20of%20Singham-owned%20Shanghai-based%20company%20have%20exchanged%20mails%20which%20expose%20their%20intent%20to%20show%20Kashmir%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20not%20part%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20attempts%20by%20these%20persons%20reveal%20their%20conspiracy%20to%20peddle%20a%20narrative%2C%20both%20globally%20and%20domestically%2C%20that%20Kashmir%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20are%20disputed%20territories.%20Their%20attempts%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20northern%20borders%20of%20India%20and%20to%20show%20Kashmir%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20not%20parts%20of%20India%20in%20maps%20amount%20to%20an%20act%20intended%20towards%20undermining%20the%20unity%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20application%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20learnt%20that%20Gautam%20Navlakha%2C%20a%20shareholder%20in%20NewsClick%2C%20remained%20involved%20in%20anti-Indian%20and%20unlawful%20activities%20such%20as%20actively%20supporting%20banned%20Naxal%20organisations%20and%20having%20anti-national%20nexus%20with%20Gulam%20Nabi%20Fai%2C%20an%20agent