the%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20raid%20was%20conducted%20on%20Tuesday%20at%2088%20locations%20in%20Delhi%20and%20seven%20in%20other%20states%20on%20the%20suspects%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20surfaced%20in%20the%20analysis%20of%20data%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20applied%20for%2015%20days'%20police%20remand%20for%20both%20the%20accused%20and%20got%20their%20custody%20for%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20sealed%20NewsClick's%20office%20in%20Delhi%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20that%2046%20suspects%20were%20questioned%20and%20digital%20devices%2C%20including%20laptops%20and%20mobile%20phones%2C%20and%20documents%20taken%20away%20for%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696445040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd81a9rd8_prabir-purkayastha_650x400_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewsclick-founder-pushed-narrative-that-kashmir-a-disputed-territory-cops-4450930%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NewsClick%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20terror%20case%2C%20allegedly%20conspired%20to%20peddle%20a%20narrative%20that%20Kashmir%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20are%20disputed%20territories%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20claimed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewsclick-founder-pushed-narrative-that-kashmir-a-disputed-territory-cops-4450930%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewsclick-founder-pushed-narrative-that-kashmir-a-disputed-territory-cops-4450930%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewsclick-founder-push