ng%20the%20flooding%20downstream.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sikkim%20government%20has%20declared%20the%20calamity%20a%20disaster%20under%20the%20Disaster%20Management%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20doom%20and%20gloom%2C%20the%20Army%20gave%20a%20heartening%20update%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20when%20it%20shared%20that%20one%20of%20the%2023%20soldiers%20that%20had%20gone%20missing%20from%20Bardang%20near%20Singtam%20town%20has%20been%20rescued%20and%20his%20condition%20is%20stable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeaths%2C%20Destruction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20government%20confirmed%20that%2010%20people%2C%20all%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20have%20died%20and%2082%20are%20still%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20many%20as%2014%20bridges%20-%20nine%20under%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20and%20five%20under%20the%20State%20government%20-%20suffered%20extensive%20damage%20and%20collapsed.%20Over%203%2C000%20tourists%20are%20feared%20stranded%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%2014%20workers%20working%20in%20Teesta%20Stage%203%20dam%20in%20Chungthang%2C%20parts%20of%20which%20were%20swept%20away%2C%20are%20still%20stranded%20in%20the%20tunnels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInjuries%20and%20missing%20persons%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20Chungthang%20in%20Mangan%20district%2C%20Dikchu%20and%20Singtam%20in%20Gangtok%20district%2C%20and%20Rangpo%20in%20Pakyong%20district.%20Over%2025%20people%20have%20been%20rushed%20to%20various%20hospitals%2C%20the%20official%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMobile%20networks%20and%20broadband%20connections%20have%20been%20disrupted%20in%20Chungthang%20and%20most%20of%20North%20Sikkim%20due%20to%20fibre%20cable%20lines%20being%20destroyed%20by%20the%20flash%20floods%20in%20Sangkalan%20and%20Toong%20in%20Mangan%20district.%20The%20police%20station%20in%20Chungthang%20has%20also%20been%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoldier%20Rescued%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTroops%20of%20Trishakti%20Corps%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20launched%20a%20massive%20search-and-rescue%20operation%20to%20trace%20the%2023%20missing%20soldiers.%20The%20search%20operations%20are%20being%20undertaken%20under%20conditions%20of%20incessant%20rains%20and%20fast-flowing%20water%20in%20the%20Teesta%20River%20with%20the%20roads%20and%20bridges%20washed%20away%20at%20many%20places.%20By%20evening%2C%20one%20soldier%20had%20been%20rescued%20and%20the%20search%20operation%20for%20the%20other%2022%20personnel%20continues%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Army%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20.%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Army%20said%20family%20members%20of%20the%20missing%20persons%20have%20been%20contacted%20and%20informed%20about%20the%20situation%20and%20all%20other%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20posted%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20North%20Bengal%20are%20safe%20and%20are%20unable%20to%20contact%20their%20family%20members%20due%20to%20disruptions%20in%20mobile%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelief%20Efforts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20government%20has%20made%20a%20request%20for%20three%20extra%20platoons%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%2C%20which%20the%20central%20government%20has%20approved.%20One%20platoon%20of%20NDRF%20is%20already%20undertaking%20relief%20and%20rescue%20efforts%20in%20Rangpo%20and%20Singtam%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20three%20additional%20NDRF%20platoons%20will%20be%20airlifted%20to%20Chungthang%20for%20rescue%20operations.%20Food%20and%20civil%20supplies%20will%20also%20be%20taken%20to%20Chungthang%20once%20the%20weather%20improves%20for%20air%20connectivity%2C%20a%20state%20government%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20import%20necessities%20from%20Siliguri%2C%20Bailey%20bridges%20will%20be%20laid%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20National%20Highways%20%26amp%3B%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Ltd%2C%20Sikkim%20Chief%20Secretary%20VB%20Pathak%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20government%20has%20also%20set%20up%2018%20relief%20camps%20in%20Singtam%2C%20Rangpo%2C%20Dikchu%20and%20Adarsh%20Gaon%2C%20which%20are%20the%20areas%20that%20have%20seen%20the%20most%20destruction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Remain%20Vigilant'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESikkim%20Chief%20Minister%20Prem%20Singh%20Tamang%20said%20he%20had%20visited%20Singtam%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20and%20urged%20everyone%20in%20the%20state%20to%20remain%20vigilant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20aware%20of%20the%20recent%20natural%20calamity%20that%20has%20struck%20our%20state.%20Emergency%20services%20have%20been%20mobilized%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20and%20I%20personally%20visited%20Singtam%20to%20assess%20the%20damages%20and%20engage%20with%20the%20local%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tamang%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20all%20aware%20of%20the%20recent%20natural%20calamity%20that%20has%20struck%20our%20state.%20Emergency%20services%20have%20been%20mobilized%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20and%20I%20personally%20visited%20Singtam%20to%20assess%20the%20damages%20and%20engage%20with%20the%20local%20community.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20I%20humbly%20urge%20all%20our%20citizens%20to%20remain%20vigilant%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKHyylID2pR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKHyylID2pR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Prem%20Singh%20Tamang%20(Golay)%20(%40PSTamangGolay)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPSTamangGolay%2Fstatus%2F1709425186959958336%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20humbly%20urge%20all%20our%20citizens%20to