rs-to-shed-poisonous-atmosphere-in-washington%2Famp_articleshow%2F104167837.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-calls-on-political-leaders-to-shed-poisonous-atmosphere-in-washington%2Famp_articleshow%2F104167837.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20In%20China%20Dies%20After%20Drinking%201%20Litre%20Alcohol%20To%20Win%20Rs%202%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20in%20China%20died%20after%20he%C2%A0drank%20a%20litre%20of%20strong%20liquor%20in%20just%2010%20minutes%20during%20a%20work%20drinking%20contest%20to%20win%20a%2020%2C000%20yuan%20(Rs%20Rs%C2%A02%2C28%2C506)%20prize%2C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3235878%2Fdeath-drinking-man-china-dies-after-speed-downing-litre-strong-liquor-office-party-bid-win-us2700%5C%22%3E%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0The%20incident%20happened%20in%20July%20when%20the%20man%2C%20identified%20as%20Zhang%2C%C2%A0attended%20his%20office's%20team-building%20dinner%2C%20where%20his%20boss%20organised%20a%20drinking%20competition.%C2%A0His%20boss%20pledged%20a%2020%2C000%20yuan%20reward%20for%20anyone%20who%20could%20outdrink%20Zhang.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Zhang%20gave%20his%20toast%20at%C2%A0Yang's%C2%A0table%2C%20the%20latter%20openly%20proposed%20a%20reward%20of%205%2C000%20yuan%20to%20anyone%20who%20could%20drink%20more%20than%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20Zhang's%C2%A0colleagues%20said.%C2%A0When%20no%20one%20responded%20he%20increased%20the%20amount%20to%2010%2C000%20yuan%20(Rs%201.15%20lakh).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZhang%20then%20asked%20about%20the%20stakes%20if%20he%20won%20the%20contest%20and%20his%20boss%20Yang%20told%20him%20he%20would%20be%20awarded%2020%2C000%20yuan.%20However%2C%20if%20he%20lost%2C%20he%20was%20asked%C2%A0to%20pay%2010%2C000%20yuan%20to%20treat%20the%20whole%20company%20to%20afternoon%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYang%C2%A0later%C2%A0chose%20several%20employees%2C%20including%20his%20own%20driver%2C%20to%20compete%20against%20Zhang.%C2%A0According%20to%20one%20of%20the%20employees%20who%20was%20at%20the%20dinner%2C%20Zhang%20downed%20a%20litre%20of%20%3Cem%3Ebaiju%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewithin%2010%20minutes.%20Notably%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBaijiu%20is%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20Chinese%20spirit%20with%20a%20typical%20alcohol%20content%20of%20between%2030%25%20to%2060%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZhang%20was%20soon%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20he%20collapsed.%20As%20per%20the%20hospital's%20critical%20condition%20notice%2C%C2%A0he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20severe%20alcohol%20poisoning%2C%20aspiration%20pneumonia%2C%20suffocation%2C%20and%20cardiac%20arrest.%20He%20died%20on%20August%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20death%2C%20a%C2%A0representative%20announced%20in%20the%20company's%20WeChat%20group%20that%20the%20company%20would%20be%20closed%20down.%C2%A0Shenzhen%20police%20are%20now%20investigating%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20there%20have%20been%20similar%20incidents%20where%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20alcohol%20poisoning.%20In%20May%20this%20year%2C%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finfluencer-dies-after-gulping-7-bottles-of-chinese-vodka-during-live-stream-4071334%5C%22%3E%20Chinese%20social%20media%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%20died%20less%20than%2012%20hours%20after%C2%A0consuming%20seven%20bottles%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBaijiu%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20Douyin%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20TikTok.%20Another%C2%A0popular%20live-streamer%20and%20influencer%20in%20China%20also%20died%20in%20June%20after%20gulping%20down%20copious%20amounts%20of%20potent%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20influencer%20named%20Zhong%20Yuan%20Huang%20Ge%20died%20on%20June%202%20after%C2%A0binging%20excessive%20amounts%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBaijiu%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0during%20a%20viral%20drinking%20challenge.%20Both%20these%20deaths%20sparked%20huge%20scrutiny%