0to%20audio%20issues%20at%20the%20venue.%20The%20comedian%2C%20in%20his%20post%2C%20promised%20to%20return%C2%A0to%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr.%20Kej%2C%20however%2C%20was%20not%20convinced%20by%20his%20note%20and%20partly%20blamed%20him%20for%20the%20show's%20failure.%20He%20noted%20that%20every%20''responsible%20and%20caring%20artist''%20does%20a%20thorough%20''soundcheck%26quot%3B%20and%20''venue%20recce''%20before%20a%20show.%20Though%20the%20musician%20acknowledged%20event%20management-related%20problems%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20shocked%20that%20Mr.%20Noah%20did%20not%20personally%20conduct%20a%20''reconnaissance''%20of%20the%20venue%2C%20or%C2%A0communicate%20the%20technical%20requirements%20and%20specifications%20to%20event%20organizers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''If%20Trevor%20Noah%20really%20bothered%20about%20his%20ticket-purchasing%20fans%2C%20then%20he%20would%20have%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20arrive%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20(or%20the%20previous%20night)%20and%20personally%20carried%20out%20a%20reconnaissance%20of%20the%20venue%2C%20tested%20out%20his%20microphone%20and%20ensured%20that%20the%20sound%20was%20optimum.%20I%20am%20sure%20he%20does%20that%20at%20other%20prestigious%20venues%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20and%20I%20am%20shocked%20to%20realize%20he%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20do%20this%20in%20Bengaluru.%20This%20is%20the%20artist's%20responsibility.%20Every%20artist%2Fcomedian%2Fband%20has%20personal%20sound%20requirements%20and%20preferences..%20and%20to%20just%20show%20up%20for%20the%20event%2C%20without%20even%20checking%20your%20sound%20is%20hugely%20irresponsible%2C''%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhile%20I%20do%20agree%20that%20there%20were%20many%20Event%20Management%20related%20problems%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20show%20f