%20will%20reach%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20said%20that%20the%20raids%20on%20persons%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20show%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20fear.%20%E2%80%9CI%20worry%20that%20from%20now%20until%20December%20(when%20five%20states%20will%20have%20elections)%20and%20May%20next%20year%20(when%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20held)%2C%20there%20may%20be%20more%20arrests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20raids%20on%20and%20arrests%20of%20journalists%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20effort%20to%20distract%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20attention%20from%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20consider%20seriously%20the%20fact%20that%20journalists%20are%20treated%20like%20terrorists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%2C%20Roy%20said%20even%20if%20people%20try%20to%20knock%20the%20issue%20out%20of%20the%20headlines%2C%20it%20has%20revealed%20the%20true%20composition%20of%20the%20country%20and%20will%20spark%20a%20revolution.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20upper%20castes%2C%20who%20constitute%20only%2015%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20are%20dominating%20in%20all%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHistorian%20Ram%20Guha%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20like%20Modi%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20also%20authoritarian.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20unlike%20Modi%2C%20she%20was%20not%20majoritarian.%20She%20did%20not%20discriminate%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%20We%20saw%20these%20kinds%20of%20regimes%20earlier%2C%20and%20they%20have%20passed.%20This%20one%20will%20pass%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E.%E2%80%9CThe%20Situation%20is%20serious%3A%20Press%20is%20under%20Pressure%E2%80%9D