ing%20his%20first%20throw%2C%20Chopra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20officials%20said%20the%20second%20athlete%20after%20me%20had%20taken%20his%20throw%20quickly.%20It%20was%20a%20bizarre%20situation.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20told%20that%20it%20was%20a%20very%20good%20throw%2C%20probably%2087-88m.%20Mentally%20you%20feel%20relieved%20if%20your%20first%20throw%20is%20very%20good.%20Later%20they%20told%20me%20I%20will%20be%20given%20another%20throw%20for%20the%20first%20attempt.%26quot%3B%20A%20perfect%20gentleman%20he%20is%2C%20Chopra%20agreed%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20have%20any%20other%20means%2C%20I%20thought%20there%20was%20no%20point%20arguing%20for%20long.%20I%20also%20thought%20it's%20affecting%20the%20competition%20of%20other%20competitors.%20The%20other%20competitors%20were%20waiting%20and%20I%20need%20to%20respect%20them%20also.%20The%20wind%20was%20blowing%20and%20everybody%20was%20feeling%20cold.%20So%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20will%20take%20the%20throw%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRule%20says%20only%20six%20throws%2C%20but%20for%20the%20first%20time%20I%20got%20seven%20throws%20in%20a%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChopra's%20next%20attempt%20measured%2082.38m.%20Jena%2C%20the%20second%20Indian%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20was%20leading%20at%20the%20halfway%20mark%20of%20three%20throws.%20But%20Chopra%20came%20up%20with%20a%20season's%20best%20throw%20of%2088.8m%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt%20to%20win%20the%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJena%20won%20the%20silver%20with%20his%20fourth%20round%20throw%20of%2087.54m.%20Jena%20booked%202024%20Olympics%20spot%2C%20for%20which%20the%20qualifying%20mark%20is%2085.50m.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChopra%20cited%20several%20other%20instances%20of%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bcheating%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20the%20red-carding%20of%20100m%20hurdler%20Jyothi%20Yarraji%20for%20false%20start%20before%20her%20medal%20was%20upgraded%20from%20bron