hi%20chief%20minister%20and%20AAP%20national%20convenor%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20illegal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20shows%20Modi%20ji%E2%80%99s%20nervousness.%20They%20will%20arrest%20many%20more%20opposition%20leaders%20till%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20is%20the%20third%20AAP%20leader%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20Last%20year%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20and%20months%20before%20that%2C%20former%20Delhi%20health%20minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20was%20also%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20mentioned%20in%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20prosecution%20complaint%20filed%20last%20year%20in%20December%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Faap-sanjay-singh-ed-raids-excise-policy-case-delhi-8967407%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20statement%20that%20was%20recorded%20before%20his%20arrest%2C%20Singh%20said%20he%20had%20raised%20his%20voice%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20stock%20market%20manipulations%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20soldiers%20of%20the%20AAP.%20We%20want%20to%20tell%20Modi%20that%20my%20arrest%20shows%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20jail%20people%20in%20a%20dictatorial%20manner%20to%20win%20elections.%20I%20want%20to%20remind%20Modi%2C%20that%20whenever%20there%20is%20injustice%2C%20we%20will%20raise%20our%20voice.%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20my%20voice%20against%20corruption%20and%20Adani%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5