as%20been%20discussing%20the%20project%20with%20various%20stakeholders%20and%20has%20already%20approached%20Kartik%20Aaryan%2C%20who%20has%20shown%20genuine%20interest%20in%20the%20project.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchak-de-india-director-shimit-amin-in-talks-with-kartik-aaryan-for-musical%2Farticleshow%2F104165572.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%20Courts%20Controversy%20With%20His%20''A%20Man%20Is%20A%20Man''%20Comment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20has%20sparked%20a%20social%20media%20debate%20with%20his%20recent%20comments%20on%C2%A0transgender%20people.%20During%20his%20closing%20speech%20at%20the%202023%20Conservative%20Party%20conference%20on%20October%204%2C%20he%20shared%20his%20stance%20on%20gender%20debate%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20man%20is%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20is%20a%20woman%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20conference%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20shouldn't%20get%20bullied%20into%20believing%20that%20people%20can%20be%20any%20sex%20they%20want%20to%20be%20-%20they%20can't.%20A%20man%20is%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20is%20a%20woman.%20That's%20just%20common%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''We%20are%20going%20to%20change%20this%20country%20and%20that%20means%2C%20life%20means%20life.%20That%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20controversial%20position.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20hard-working%20people%20agree%20with%20it.%C2%A0It%20also%20shouldn't%20be%20controversial%20for%20parents%20to%20know%20what%20their%20children%20are%20learning%20in%20school%20about%20relationships.%20Patients%20should%20know%20when%20hospitals%20are%20talking%20about%20men%20or%20women%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECouldn't%20believe%20it%20when%20I%20heard%20these%20words%20coming%20out%20his%20mouth%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%9CWe%20shouldn't%20be%20bullied%20into%20thinking%20anyone%20can%20be%20any%20sex%20that%20they%20want%20to%20be.%20A%20man%20is%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20is%20a%20woman%2C%20that%20is%20just%20common%20sense.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Transphobic%20much%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Ftrans%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23trans%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRishiSunak%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RishiSunak%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPoliticsLive%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PoliticsLive%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fsv3butBaad%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fsv3butBaad%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Julia%20M%20(%40Julia_Milligan1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJulia_Milligan1%2Fstatus%2F1709539457068622104%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThough%20some%20supported%20his%20views%2C%20many%20were%20angry%20for%20making%20''disrespectful''%20comments%20towards%20the%20transgender%20community.%20Some%20mocked%20him%20saying%20that%20his%20remarks%20are%20far%20away%20from%20''common%20sense.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20said%2C%20''The%20persistent%20attacks%20on%20not%20only%20one%20of%20the%20smallest%20but%20most%20at-risk%20communities%20are%20vile.%20Absolutely%20disgusting%20party%20through%20and%20through%20including%20anyone%20who%20supports%20them.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''I'm%20so%20fed%20up%20with%20Sunak%20talking%20up%20the%20importance%20of%20maths%2C%20yet%20his%20biology%20knowledge%20is%20so%20poor.%20Biological%20sex%20is%20so%20complicated%20and%20interesting%20and%20not%20at%20all%2