0necessary%20documents%20and%20travel%20permissions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20UN%20figures%20reviewed%20by%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20around%201.3%20million%20Afghans%20are%20registered%20refugees%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20880%2C000%20more%20have%20legal%20status%20to%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20increasingly%20harsh%20rhetoric%20in%20Pakistan%20against%20Afghan%20refugees%20comes%20after%20an%20uptick%20in%20violence%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-warns-afghan-taliban-against-harboring-militants%2Fa-66240251%5C%22%3ETehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20group%20with%20links%20to%20the%20hardline%C2%A0Taliban%C2%A0Sunni%20militants%20who%20retook%20power%20in%20Afghanistan%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20TTP%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20overthrow%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20rule%20with%20its%20strict%20interpretation%20of%20Islamic%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Afghans%20have%20entered%20Pakistan%20over%20the%20years%2C%20following%20successive%20wars%20and%20authoritarian%20regimes.%20Some%20600%2C000%20arrived%20since%20August%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20Afghans%20are%20on%20waiting%20lists%20to%20get%20Pakistani%20visas%2C%20but%20the%20process%20can%20take%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-orders-illegal-migrant-afghans-to-leave-country%2Fa-66988742%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696428944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04191718%2F49869773933_4581459b7d_k2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fafghan-taliban-urges-pakistan-to-reconsider-ultimatum-to-undocumented-immigrants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20decision%20to%20expel%20undocumented%20immigrants%20came%20amid%20claims%20it%20mad