or-not-ensuring-elections-on-time-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F104163848.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khan-unhappy-with-pakistan-president-alvi-for-not-ensuring-elections-on-time-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F104163848.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'If%20the%20Ruler%20Is%20Defender%20of%20Faith%2C%20What%20Does%20Secularism%20Do%3F'%3A%20Justice%20Muralidhar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04185619%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20celebrated%20retired%20chief%20justice%20of%20a%20high%20court%20and%20a%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20held%20forth%20on%20threats%20to%20the%20concepts%20of%20secularism%20and%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%20at%20a%20gathering%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20October%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConstitutional%20functionaries%20should%20stay%20within%20their%20powers%20and%20better%20not%20go%20overboard%2C%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20Justice%20L.%20Nageswara%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Rao%20was%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20national%20seminar%20on%20%E2%80%98constitution%20and%20we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%2C%20organised%20by%20All%20India%20Lawyers%20Union%E2%80%99s%20Telangana%20Committee%20and%20spoke%20on%20revisiting%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%20The%20event%20also%20had%20as%20guest%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Odisha%20high%20court%2C%20Justice%20S.%20Muralidhar%2C%20who%20delivered%20a%20scathing%20speech%20on%20current%20threats%20to%20secularism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeven%20hundred%20delegates%20from%20across%20Telangana%20participated%20in%20the%20day-long%20seminar%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20Kolli%20Satyanarayana%20who%20heads%20the%20All%20India%20Lawyers%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJustice%20Muralidhar%20on%20secularism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20S.%20Muralidhar%2C%20delivered%20a%20lecture%20on%20secularism%20and%20seven%20decades%20of%20its%20judicial%20interpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20pervading%20fear%20now%20in%20speak%20out%20which%20amounted%20to%20self%20censorship.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20journalists%20start%20to%20write%20what%20is%20liked%20by%20their%20masters%20it%20is%20death%20knell%20of%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20India%20is%20not%20a%20theocratic%20state.%20Unlike%20Pakistan%2C%20India%20exercised%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20be%20secular%2C%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%20we%20have%20to%20understand%20Indian%20nature%20of%20secularism%20which%20could%20be%20different%20from%20countries%20like%20that%20of%20the%20USA%20and%20France.%20Article%2025%20and%2026%20speak%20of%20religions%20tolerance.%20This%20kind%20of%20secularism%20is%20one%20of%20the%20basic%20features%20of%20our%20constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20while%20parliaments%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20gain%20the%20power%20to%20amend%20to%20this%20basic%20feature%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20recognises%20secularism%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98cohesive%2C%20unified%2C%20%5Band%5D%20casteless%20society%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stressed%20that%20caste%20is%20also%20a%20major%20threat%20to%20secularism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20judge%2C%20known%20for%20celebrated%20judgments%2C%20said%20that%20in%20our%20current%20public%20discourse%2C%20this%20notion%20of%20secularism%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Cseriously%20challenged%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChief%20Ministers%20donating%20public%20funds%20to%20religions%20temples%20is%20one%20such%20thing.%20Political%20persons%20are%20associating%20themselves%20with%20%3Cem%3Eyagnas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eyagas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20other%20such%20functions%20and%20endorsing%20them%20in%20public%20functions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuoting%20an%20example%20from%20Nehru%20he%20said%20that%20earlier%20public%20representatives%20never%20allowed%20religious%20practices%20in%20public%20institutions.%20But%20now%20the%20political%20climate%20is%20changing%20and%20posing%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20what%20we%20inherited%20as%20secularism%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%2C%20crucially%2C%20said%20that%20issuing%20a%20mandamus%20to%20construct%20a%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20even%20without%20a%20prayer%20by%20the%20parties%20to%20the%20case%20triggers%20myriad%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20levels%20of%20the%20tolerance.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20ruler%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20defender%20of%20the%20faith%20what%20does%20secularism%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20wondered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20non-elevation%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20despite%20the%20SC%20Collegium%20advocating%20it%2C%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20debates%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20overreach%20into%20judicial%20appointments%20and%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-muralidhar-supreme-court-collegium-oped%5C%22%3Ecriticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-muralidhar-supreme-court-collegium-oped%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20spirited%20editorial%20on%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20legal%20luminaries%20had%20noted%20that%20among%20key%20judgements%20that%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20authored%20is%20the%20Naz%20Foundation%20one%20that%20decriminalised%20consensual%20homosexuality%2C%20the%20conviction%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20for%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%2C%20the%20sentencing%20of%2016%20policemen%20for%20the%20killings%20of%2038%20Muslims%20in%20Hashimpura%20and%20the%20bail%20to%20Gautam%20Navlakha%2C%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%20The%20authors%20spoke%20also%20on%20how%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20him%20ensured%20ambulance%20services%20to%20riot-affected%20areas%20in%20northeast%20Delhi%20in%202020%2C%20through%20a%20late%20night%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20John%20Brittas%2C%20also%20a%20speaker%20at%20the%20event%2C%20spoke%20on%20how%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20was%20not%20elevated%20for%20reasons%20not%20confined%20to%20judicial%20parameters%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJustice%20Rao%20on%20basic%20structure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%20noted%20that%20Justice%20Rao%2C%20narrating%20the%20background%20of%20the%20famous%20%3Cem%3EKesavananda%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EBharati%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%20said%20that%20the%20tussle%20between%20government%20and%20courts%20is%20healthy%20as%20long%20as%20they%20maintain%20a%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20403px)%2085vw%2C%20403px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04192024%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-03-at-8.00.14-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22403%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04192024%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-03-at-8.00.14-PM.jpeg%20745w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04192024%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-03-at-8.00.14-PM-257x300.jpeg%20257w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678292%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22470%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJustice%20L.%20Nageswar%20Rao.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20realising%20the%20directive%20principles%20is%20primarily%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20and%20hence%20they%20make%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20courts%20interfere%20wherever%20they%20feel%20fundamental%20rights%20are%20trampled%20upon%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuoting%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Justice%20Rao%20said%20that%20Article%2032%2C%20the%20heart%20and%20soul%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20preserves%20the%20right%20of%20judicial%20review.%20He%20also%20quoted%20Thomas%20Jefferson%20in%20pointing%20out%20that%20every%20generation%20has%20a%20right%20to%20decide%20what%E2%80%99s%20good%20for%20them%20but%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20abrogate%20the%20constitution.%20The%20essential%20elements%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ecan%E2%80%99t%20be%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Etouched%20upon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Rao%20also%20affirmed%20that%20the%20preamble%20is%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20constitution.%20He%20cited%20Israel%20and%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20example%20on%20efforts%20to%20take%20away%20powers%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20March%202023%2C%20powers%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20Israel%20curtailed%20by%20bringing%20an%20amendment%20to%20its%20basic%20law%20and%20by%20introducing%20an%20overriding%20clause.%20According%20to%20this%20clause%2C%20the%20parliament%20can%20over%20ride%20the%20directives%2C%20orders%20and%20judgements%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20if%20the%20parliament%20wishes%20so.%20The%20amendment%20also%20gave%20right%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20by%20changing%20the%20number%20of%20persons%20to%20be%20appointed%20from%20the%20executive.%20This%20overshoot%20angered%20the%20Israel%20citizens%20and%20who%20had%20been%20demonstrating%20for%2036%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20questioning%20%E2%80%9Chow%20many%20of%20us%20in%20India%20would%20take%20to%20such%20a%20recourse%20of%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20if%20similar%20thing%20happened%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20discretionary%20powers%20of%20speakers%20and%20governors%2C%20Justice%20Rao%20said%20that%20the%20former%20is%20not%20independent%20anymore%20and%20the%20latter%20sit%20on%20files.%20They%20should%20not%20go%20overboard%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20war%20cry%20of%20politicians%20who%20desire%20parliamentary%20supremacy%20over%20the%20other%20organs%20should%20be%20looked%20at%20with%20suspicion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696427546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04185619%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-the-ruler-is-defender-of-faith-what-does-secularism-do-justice-muralidhar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20judge%2C%20known%20for%20celebrated%20judgments%2C%20said%20that%20in%20our%20current%20public%20discourse%2C%20this%20notion%20of%20secularism%20is%20being%20'seriously%20challenged.'%20Former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20L.%20Nageswara%20Rao%20also%20spoke%20at%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-the-ruler-is-defender-of-faith-what-does-secularism-do-justice-muralidhar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Fought%20for%20what%20I%20believed%20in'%3A%20McCarthy%20bows%20out%2C%20calls%20dissenting%20Republicans%20'phony%20conservatives%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696427412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104164384%2Cimgsize-779313.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffought-for-what-i-believed-in-mccarthy-bows-out-calls-dissenting-republicans-phony-conservatives%2Farticleshow%2F104164350.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104164350.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20historic%20move%2C%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20was%20ousted%20from%20his%20position%20by%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20in%20a%20vote%20of%20216-210.%20All%20208%20Democrats%20and%20eight%20Republicans%