or-digital-premiere-on-october-6-after-rs-500-crore-haul-at-box-office%2Farticleshow%2F104163709.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20Than%20100%20Sitting%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20Have%20Declared%20Cases%20of%20Hate%20Speech%2C%20Most%20From%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F14154412%2Fhate-speech.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20total%20of%20107%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20have%20declared%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech%20against%20them%2C%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20them%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20revealed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadrindia.org%2Fcontent%2Fanalysis-sitting-mpsmlas-declared-cases-related-hate-speech-0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20compiled%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20and%20National%20Election%20Watch%20(NEW)%2C%20was%20released%20on%20Tuesday.%20It%20has%20been%20compiled%20by%20analysing%20the%20self-sworn%20affidavits%20of%20all%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20that%20were%20filed%20prior%20to%20the%20last%20election%20they%20contested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20hate%20speech%20has%20not%20been%20defined%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Law%20Commission%20Report%20no%20267%3B%20Sections%20153(A)%2C%20153(B)%2C%20295(A)%2C%20298%2C%20505(1)%20and%20505%20(2)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20deal%20with%20hate%20speech.%20In%20addition%2C%20Section%208%2C%20Section%20123%20(3A)%20and%20Section%20125%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%20also%20deal%20with%20candidates%20whose%20acts%20amount%20to%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%2033%20of%20the%20total%20763%20sitting%20MPs%20and%2074%20of%20the%20total%204%2C005%20sitting%20MLAs%20whose%20self-sworn%20affidavits%20were%20analysed%2C%20have%20declared%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20most%20number%20of%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20with%20declared%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20of%20the%2033%20sitting%20MPs%20who%20declared%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech%2C%2022%20are%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20parties%20with%20MPs%20with%20declared%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech%20include%20two%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20one%20each%20from%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20AIMIM%2C%20AIUDF%2C%20DMK%2C%20MDMK%2C%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%2C%20Viduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%20and%20one%20independent%20MP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2074%20MLAs%20who%20declared%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech%2C%2020%20are%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20parties%20with%20MLAs%20with%20declared%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech%20include%2013%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20six%20from%20the%20AAP%2C%20five%20each%20from%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20four%20each%20from%20the%20DMK%20and%20the%20RJD%2C%20three%20each%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20two%20from%20AIUDF%20and%201%20each%20from%20AIMIM%2C%20CPI(M)%2C%20NCP%2C%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20TDP%2C%20Tipra%20Motha%20Party%20and%20BRS.%20Two%20independent%20MLAs%20also%20have%20cases%20relating%20to%20hate%20speech%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhate-speech-bjp-anti-muslim-2023%5C%22%3E80%25%20of%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%20Speech%20in%202023%20Was%20Delivered%20in%20BJP-Ruled%20States%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20states%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20tops%20the%20list%20with%20seven%20sitting%20MPs%20having%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20four%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20three%20each%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Telangana.%20Two%20MPs%20each%20are%20from%20Assam%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20West%20Bengal%20while%20one%20MP%20each%20from%20Jharkhand%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Punjab%20have%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20MLAs%2C%20nine%20are%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20each.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20there%20are%20six%20MLAs%20each%20with%20declared%20criminal%20cases%20of%20hate%20speech%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Telangana%2C%20five%20each%20from%20Assam%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20There%20are%20four%20MLAs%20each%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20and%20three%20each%20from%20Jharkhand%20and%20Uttarakhand.%20Two%20MLAs%20each%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Tripura%20have%20declared%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech%20along%20with%20one%20MLA%20each%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Odisha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20a%20total%20of%20480%20candidates%20with%20declared%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech%20have%20contested%20elections%20for%20state%20assemblies%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20giving%20tickets%20to%20candidates%20who%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech%20especially%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20religious%20groups%20and%20for%20committing%20acts%20that%20are%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%2C%20political%20parties%20have%20been%20in%20a%20way%20abetting%20circumstances%20that%20lead%20to%20events%20such%20as%20communal%20riots%20and%20violence%20between%20different%20groups%20of%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuris-slurs-were-an-attack-on-the-constitution-of-india%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20Slurs%20Were%20an%20Attack%20on%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EADR%20said%20it%20supports%20some%20recommendations%20made%20by%20the%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20to%20control%20hate%20speech.%20It%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHate%20speech%20poses%20complex%20challenges%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%20Hence%2C%20new%20provisions%20in%20IPC%20are%20required%20to%20be%20incorporated%20to%20address%20this%20issue.%20Amendments%20to%20the%20IPC%2C%201860%20and%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%20by%20adding%20new%20provisions%20on%20%E2%80%98Prohibiting%20incitement%20to%20hatred%E2%80%99%20provocation%20of%20violence%20in%20certain%20cases%E2%80%99%20following%20section%20505%20IPC%2C%20and%20accordingly%20amending%20the%20First%20Schedule%20of%20CrPC%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EADR%20said%20strict%20action%20must%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20candidates%20giving%20hate%20speech%20prior%2C%20during%20and%20after%20elections%20if%20found%20guilty%20of%20hate%20speech.%20It%20said%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20been%20misused%20by%20political%20parties%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%E2%80%9D%20statements.%20%E2%80%9CHence%2C%20it%20is%20recommended%20that%20such%20unlawful%20statements%20on%20online%20platforms%20should%20be%20monitored%20and%20if%20the%20person%20found%20guilty%2C%20they%20should%20be%20penalised%2C%E2%80%9D%20ADR%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696425054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F14154412%2Fhate-speech.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhate-speech-cases-107-sitting-mps-mlas-adr-analysis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20analysis%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%2033%20of%20the%20total%20763%20sitting%20MPs%20and%2074%20of%20the%204%2C005%20sitting%20MLAs%20are%20facing%20cases%20related%20to%20hate%20speech.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%2042%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20are%20from%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhate-speech-cases-107-sitting-mps-mlas-adr-analysis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Hockey%20Wali%E2%80%99%20Sarpanch%20Helps%20Girls%20Smash%20Patriarchy%20With%20Sports%2C%20Grit%20%26amp%3B%20Hope%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENeeru%20Yadav%20wanted%20to%20play%20hockey%20but%20was%20asked%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20education%20by%20her%20family.%20When%20she%20became%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331323%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-2023-nari-shakti-vandan-adhiniyam-pramila-dandavate-modi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewoman%20sarpanch%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Lambi%20Ahir%20village%20in%202020%2C%20she%20started%20helping%20other%20girls%20fulfill%20their%20hockey%20dreams%20by%20forming%20a%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGirls%20of%20the%20Lambi%20Ahir%20village%20in%20Rajasthan%20were%20married%20early%20and%20playing%20a%20sport%20was%20out%20of%20question.%20When%20she%20became%20a%20sarpanch%2C%20Neeru%20heard%20stories%20of%20a%20few%20girls%20who%20dreamt%20of%20playing%20hockey%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebett