2https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20raids%20on%20and%20questionings%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%2046%20journalists%2C%20editors%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20professionals%20seemingly%20connected%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%20to%20the%20online%20news%20portal%2C%20%3Ci%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fi%3E.%20Several%20of%20the%20journalists%E2%80%99%20electronic%20devices%20were%20seized%20and%20the%20portal%E2%80%99s%20director%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20its%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20has%20sought%20the%20courts%E2%80%99%20help%20in%20framing%20of%20norms%20to%20discourage%20the%20seizure%20of%20journalists%E2%80%99%20phones%20and%20laptops%20on%20a%20whim%2C%20evolving%20guidelines%20for%20the%20interrogation%20of%20journalists%20and%20for%20seizures%20from%20them%20and%20finding%20ways%20to%20ensure%20the%20accountability%20of%20state%20agencies%20and%20individual%20officers%20who%20are%20found%20overstepping%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisations%2C%20including%20press%20clubs%20of%20various%20cities%2C%20note%20that%20they%20do%20not%20wish%20for%20journalists%20to%20be%20above%20the%20law%20but%20only%20that%20they%20be%20treated%20in%20accordance%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20their%20letter%20is%20given%20below.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ED.Y.%20Chandrachud%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOctober%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDear%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20write%20this%20letter%20as%20a%20voluntary%20and%20free%20coalition%20of%20organisations%20that%20represent%20the%20free%20press%20and%20who%20are%20committed%20to%20upholding%20the%20values%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20letter%20is%20an%20earnest%20plea%20to%20the%20sentinel%20on%20the%20%3Ci%3Equi%20vive%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20weather-beaten%20as%20that%20phrase%20may%20have%20become%E2%80%94an%20appeal%20from%20one%20institution%20that%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20exercise%20of%20freedom%20and%20democracy%20in%20India%2C%20to%20one%20that%20is%20Supreme%20and%20is%20sworn%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution%20that%20enshrines%20those%20freedoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20write%20this%20letter%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20addressed%20not%20just%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20but%20to%20an%20incumbent%20who%20has%20said%2C%20within%20the%20court%20and%20outside%2C%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpress%20has%20a%20duty%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20and%20present%20citizens%20with%20hard%20facts%20enabling%20them%20to%20make%20choices%20that%20propel%20democracy%20in%20the%20right%20direction%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedoms%20will%20be%20safe%20as%20long%20as%20journalists%20can%20play%20this%20role%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20being%20chilled%20by%20a%20threat%20of%20reprisal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20today%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20journalists%20in%20India%20finds%20itself%20working%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20reprisal.%20And%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20Judiciary%20confronts%20Power%20with%20a%20fundamental%20Truth%E2%80%94that%20there%20is%20a%20Constitution%20to%20which%20we%20are%20all%20answerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%203%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20raided%20the%20homes%20of%2046%20journalists%2C%20editors%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20professionals%20seemingly%20connected%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%20to%20the%20online%20news%20portal%2C%20%3Ci%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20raids%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20two%20persons%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%20mobile%20phones%20and%20computers%20without%20ensuring%20the%20integrity%20of%20their%20data%E2%80%94a%20basic%20protocol%20that%20is%20essential%20to%20due%20process.%20The%20invocation%20of%20UAPA%20is%20especially%20chilling.%20%3Cspan%3EJournalism%20cannot%20be%20prosecuted%20as%20%E2%80%98terrorism%E2%80%99.%20Enough%20instances%20in%20history%20abound%20to%20tell%20us%20where%20that%20eventually%20goes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20your%20time%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20you%20have%20seen%20how%20on%20numerous%20occasions%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20investigating%20agencies%20have%20been%20misused%20and%20weaponised%20against%20the%20Press.%20Sedition%20and%20terrorism%20cases%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20editors%20and%20reporters%2C%20and%20multiple%2C%20sequential%20and%2For%20frivolous%20FIRs%20have%20been%20used%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20harassment%20against%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20addressing%20this%20letter%20to%20you%20is%20not%20to%20bypass%20or%20circumvent%20the%20process%20and%20procedure%20established%20by%20law.%20But%20when%20journalists%20are%20summoned%20and%20their%20devices%20seized%20in%20the%20name%20of%20investigation%2C%20there%20is%20an%20inherent%20malice%20in%20the%20process%20that%20must%20be%20checked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04164330%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-4.32.24-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04164330%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-4.32.24-PM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04164330%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-4.32.24-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678257%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJournalists%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20at%20the%20release%20of%20the%20joint%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20police%20are%20obliged%20by%20the%20Constitution%20to%20state%20the%20grounds%20of%20arrest%2C%20it%20must%20equally%20be%20a%20precondition%20to%20questioning.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20as%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20%3Ci%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fi%3E%20case%2C%20vague%20assertions%20about%20the%20investigation%20of%20some%20unspecified%20offence%20have%20become%20the%20grounds%20for%20questioning%20journalists%20about%20their%20coverage%20of%2C%20%3Ci%3Einter%20alia%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20say%20that%20journalists%20are%20above%20the%20law.%20We%20are%20not%20and%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20be.%20However%2C%20intimidation%20of%20the%20media%20affects%20the%20democratic%20fabric%20of%20society.%20And%20subjecting%20journalists%20to%20a%20concentrated%20criminal%20process%20because%20the%20government%20disapproves%20of%20their%20coverage%20of%20national%20and%20international%20affairs%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20chill%20the%20press%20by%20threat%20of%20reprisal%E2%80%94the%20very%20ingredient%20you%20identified%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWide%20powers%20of%20investigation%20are%20given%20to%20the%20state%20on%20the%20assumption%20of%20bonafides%20on%20the%20part%20of%20its%20agencies.%20Equally%2C%20a%20wide%20immunity%20against%20coercion%20must%20be%20read%20into%20the%20constitutional%20provisions%20of%20free%20speech%2C%20and%20methods%20must%20be%20devised%20against%20police%20overreach%E2%80%94especially%20given%20the%20repeated%20misuse%20of%20these%20powers.%20Far%20too%20much%20is%20at%20stake%20to%20test%20every%20case%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20trial%20which%20can%20last%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJournalists%20arrested%20under%20UAPA%20can%20end%20up%20spending%20months%2C%20if%20not%20years%2C%20behind%20bars%20before%20they%20are%20even%20granted%20bail.%20We%20already%20have%20the%20case%20of%20Siddique%20Kappan%20before%20us%3B%20he%20was%20incarcerated%20for%20two%20years%20and%20four%20months%20before%20finally%20securing%20bail.%20The%20tragic%20death%20of%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%20in%20custody%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20indifferent%20the%20authorities%20seem%20to%20have%20become%20towards%20human%20life%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20combating%20%E2%80%98terrorism%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20fear%20is%20that%20state%20actions%20against%20the%20media%20have%20been%20taken%20beyond%20measure%2C%20and%20should%20they%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20direction%20they%20are%20headed%2C%20it%20may%20be%20too%20late%20for%20corrective%20or%20remedial%20steps.%20It%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20our%20collective%20view%20that%20the%20Higher%20Judiciary%20must%20now%20intervene%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20increasingly%20repressive%20use%20of%20investigating%20agencies%20against%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20we%20would%20be%20obliged%20if%20the%20courts%20would%20consider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20framing%20of%20norms%20to%20discourage%20the%20seizure%20of%20journalists%E2%80%99%20phones%20and%20laptops%20on%20a%20whim%2C%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20seized%20of%20this%20issue%20in%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20noted%20academics%E2%80%94%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ERam%20Ramaswamy%20%26amp%3B%20Ors.%3C%2Fi%3E%20v.%20%3Ci%3EUnion%20of%20India%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%2C%20W.P.%20(Crl)%20No.%20138%2F2021%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20not%20been%20satisfied%20by%20the%20affidavits%20filed%20by%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20in%20these%20proceedings.%20While%20the%20wheels%20of%20justice%20have%20been%20turning%2C%20the%20State%20has%20continued%20to%20act%20with%20impunity.%20The%20seizure%20of%20devices%20compromises%20our%20professional%20work.%20As%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20itself%20has%20observed%20(in%20the%20%3Ci%3EPegasus%3C%2Fi%3E%20matter)%2C%20the%20protection%20of%20sources%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20and%20necessary%20corollary%E2%80%9D%20of%20freedom%20of%20media.%20But%20laptops%20and%20phones%20are%20no%20longer%20just%20official%20tools%20used%20to%20conduct%20official%20business.%20They%20have%20fundamentally%20become%20an%20extension%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20self.%20These%20devices%20are%20integrated%20into%20our%20entire%20lives%20and%20have%20vital%20personal%20information%20contained%20in%20them%E2%80%94from%20communication%20to%20photographs%20to%20conversations%20with%20family%20and%20friends.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20or%20justification%20that%20investigating%20agencies%20should%20have%20access%20to%20such%20material.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EEvolving%20guidelines%20for%20the%20interrogation%20of%20journalists%20and%20for%20seizures%20from%20them%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20are%20not%20undertaken%20as%20fishing%20expeditions%20with%20no%20bearing%20to%20an%20actual%20offence.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EFinding%20ways%20to%20ensure%20the%20accountability%20of%20State%20agencies%20and%20individual%20officers%20who%20are%20found%20overstepping%20the%20law%20or%20willfully%20misleading%20courts%20with%20vague%20and%20open-ended%20investigations%20against%20journalists%20for%20their%20journalistic%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%2C%20write%20this%20letter%20to%20your%20lordship%20after%20considerable%20thought%20and%20contemplation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20many%20instances%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20when%20assaults%20on%20the%20free%20press%20by%20the%20State%20have%20required%20judicial%20intervention%2C%20and%20we%20continue%20to%20pursue%20such%20cases.%20But%20the%20developments%20over%20the%20past%2024%20hours%20have%20left%20us%20no%20option%20but%20to%20appeal%20to%20your%20good%20conscience%20to%20take%20cognisance%20and%20intervene%20before%20it%20is%20too%20late%20and%20an%20autocratic%20police%20state%20becomes%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20journalists%20and%20news%20professionals%2C%20we%20are%20always%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20any%20bona%20fide%20investigation.%20However%2C%20ad%20hoc%2C%20sweeping%20seizures%20and%20interrogations%20surely%20cannot%20be%20considered%20acceptable%20in%20any%20democratic%20country%2C%20let%20alone%20one%20that%20has%20begun%20advertising%20itself%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98mother%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDigipub%20News%20India%20Foundation%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Press%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPress%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFoundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetwork%20of%20Women%20in%20Media%2C%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChandigarh%20Press%20Club%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENational%20Alliance%20of%20Journalists%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKerala%20Union%20of%20Working%20Journalists%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrihanmumbai%20Union%20of%20Journalists%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFree%20Speech%20Collective%2C%20Mumbai%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Press%20Club%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArunachal%20Pradesh%20Union%20of%20Working%20Journalists%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPress%20Association%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGauhati%20Press%20Club%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20Journalists%20Union%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Press%20Club%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20News%20Camermen%E2%80%99s%20Association%20(WNCA)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696417549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.