ds%2F2020%2F11%2F16133352%2Fkapil-sibal-congress.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20raucous%20debate%20around%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll%E2%80%99%20and%20other%20electoral%20amendments%20and%20reforms%2C%20a%20significant%20electoral%20transgression%20that%20is%20studiously%20ignored%20and%20always%20put%20aside%20is%20the%20unsettled%20issue%20of%20declaring%20booth-wise%20results%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(EC).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20knowing%20how%20a%20booth%2C%20which%20represents%20a%20clutch%20of%20streets%2C%20has%20voted%20not%20only%20goes%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20secret%20ballot%20but%20is%20lethal%20and%20destructive%20when%20threats%2C%20harassment%20and%20intimidation%20are%20used%20by%20political%20parties%20to%20force%20a%20voter%20to%20go%20their%20way.%20The%20only%20safeguard%20is%20to%20get%20a%20totaliser%2C%20which%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20the%20EC%20to%20be%20attached%20to%20the%20EVM.%20Eminent%20lawyer%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20first%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20now%20with%20ally%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20outlines%20the%20road%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20the%20interview%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20agree%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20from%202008%2C%20to%20get%20totalisers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20changed%20today%2C%20and%20unfortunately%20that%20recommendation%20which%20was%20extremely%20significant%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20ensure%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20the%20EC%20today%20is%20in%20complete%20alignment%20with%20the%20present%20government.%20So%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20expect%20anything%20from%20the%20EC%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotalisers%20are%20crucial%20as%20they%20prevent%20political%20parties%20from%20getting%20booth-wise%20results%2C%20which%20goes%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20secret%20ballot%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20for%20electoral%20fairness%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20political%20parties%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20manipulate%20results%2C%20and%20a%20totaliser%20would%20have%20ensured%20that%20political%20parties%20have%20no%20access%20to%20find%20out%20how%20citizens%20have%20voted%20and%20for%20which%20party%20in%20any%20particular%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20totaliser%20in%20an%20EVM%20mixes%20up%20votes%2C%20like%20in%20the%20pre-EVM%20age%20of%20paper%20ballots%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20impossible%20to%20find%20out%20how%20a%20booth%20voted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20EVMs%2C%20ballot%20papers%20could%20be%20mixed%20if%20there%20was%20any%20apprehension%20of%20intimidation%20of%20voters.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20political%20parties%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20booth-wise%20results%2C%20they%20cannot%20pressurise%20or%20threaten%20those%20particular%20voters%20of%20the%20locality%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20vote%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20EC%20recommendation%20came%20when%20your%20government%20UPA%20II%20was%20in%20power%2C%20but%20nothing%20happened%20despite%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20committee%20was%20set%20up%20in%202009%2C%20but%20it%20reached%20nowhere%E2%80%A6%20however%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20Congress%20party%20would%20have%20opposed%20the%20idea%2C%20most%20political%20parties%20and%20allies%20were%20in%20alignment%20with%20this%20recommendation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20think%20we%20really%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20the%20significance%20or%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20necessity%20then%2C%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20situation%20came%20to%20us%20later%2C%20in%202014%20after%20the%20new%20government%20came%20to%20power.%20It%20has%20been%20stonewalling%20the%20recommendation%20of%20totalisers%20and%20has%20not%20come%20forward%20to%20support%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20August%202014%2C%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20EC%20moved%20the%20law%20ministry%20yet%20again%2C%20but%20it%20was%20only%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20took%20note%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20PIL%20in%20September%20the%20same%20year%2C%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20in%20the%20spotlight%20again.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20correct%2C%20the%20PIL%20has%20been%20asking%20the%20government%20what%20it%20intends%20to%20do%3B%20after%20all%2C%20the%20EC%20can%E2%80%99t%20formally%20say%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20its%20own%20recommendations.%20The%20EC%20today%20is%20obviously%20not%20pushing%20for%20it%2C%20nor%20is%20the%20government%20very%20keen%20on%20it%20and%20the%20issue%20is%20lying%20in%20limbo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20January%202017%2C%20a%20group%20of%20ministers%20headed%20by%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20that%20included%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20Manohar%20Parrikar%20and%20others%2C%20rejected%20the%20introduction%20of%20totalisers%20saying%20booth%20management%20helps%20parties%20to%20be%20responsive%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20needs.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20GoP%20rejected%20totalisers%20saying%20machines%20are%20involved%20and%20so%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20interfere%2C%20and%20other%20reasons%20mentioned%20above%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20mention%20(of%20the%20danger)%20of%20knowing%20voter%20results.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20this%20government%20is%20not%20at%20all%20keen%20on%20totalisers%20because%20it%20wants%20to%20collect%20booth%20data%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20pressurising%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20the%20well-known%20case%20where%20BJP%20MP%20Maneka%20Gandhi%20publicly%20said%20at%20election%20rallies%20that%20development%20will%20be%20cut%20off%20going%20by%20booth%20results.%20So%20did%20Tejasvi%20Surya%2C%20who%20showed%20how%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20vote%2C%20from%20booth%20results.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20tactics%20they%20use%20to%20manipulate%20the%20results%2C%20and%20pollute%20the%20election%20process.%20The%20BJP%20or%20any%20political%20party%20knows%20from%20booth-wise%20results%20that%20in%20this%20particular%20area%2C%20the%20voters%20are%20with%20us%20or%20against%20us.%20Post-election%20too%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20easy%20to%20find%20out%20voting%20trends%20from%20booth%20results%2C%20politicians%20can%20intimidate%20and%20threaten%20as%20Maneka%20warned%20voters%20during%20her%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20ways%20to%20cut%20out%20your%20anti-vote%20by%20looking%20at%20past%20voting%20trends%20from%20booths%20%E2%80%93%20eliminate%20or%20delete%20names%20from%20electoral%20rolls%3B%20only%20one%20Aadhaar%20card%20is%20reflected%20and%20not%20of%20the%20others%20in%20a%20family%3B%20then%20they%20find%20homes%20that%20have%20been%20vacated%20but%20members%20are%20still%20on%20the%20voter%20rolls%20and%20votes%20are%20cast%20in%20their%20names%20after%205%20pm%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20person%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20polling%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManipulation%20of%20EVMs%20is%20a%20very%20unpopular%20allegation%20because%20nobody%20can%20actually%20prove%20it%2C%20but%20either%20way%2C%20the%20presumption%20is%20that%20any%20machine%20can%20be%20manipulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20also%20have%20a%20prime%20minister%20today%20who%20blows%20up%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20of%20taxpayers%E2%80%99%20money%20on%20his%20election%20campaigns.%20Does%20that%20give%20him%20an%20unfair%20advantage%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsn%E2%80%99t%20it%20up%20to%20the%20EC%20to%20take%20note%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%3F%20If%20institutional%20processes%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20then%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20do%20what%20he%20wants%20to%20do%2C%20unhindered.%20The%20institutional%20processes%20in%20this%20country%20have%20been%20dismantled%2C%20so%20obviously%20there%20is%20no%20institutional%20check%20on%20activities.%20Every%20institutional%20structure%20has%20been%20systematically%20dismantled%2C%20including%20of%20course%2C%20the%20EC%2C%20which%20is%20a%20collaborator%20in%20this%20enterprise%20today.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20the%20EC%20watching%20with%20complete%20disregard%20when%20in%20one%20constituency%20the%20voting%20is%20going%20on%20and%20next%20door%2C%20in%20another%20state%20where%20the%20election%20is%20going%20on%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20making%20an%20election%20appeal%20which%20is%20being%20televised.%20The%20EC%20is%20quiet%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20send%20notices%20when%20ministers%20and%20political%20leaders%20make%20disparaging%20remarks%20and%20threaten%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%20too%20is%20a%20very%20active%20collaborator%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20these%20are%20institutional%20structures%20that%20have%20been%20dismantled%20for%20reasons%20of%20greed%20%E2%80%93%20for%20high%20TRPs%2C%20and%20where%20industrial%20houses%20which%20own%20the%20media%20seek%20favours%20from%20the%20government%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20too%20much%20hope%20in%20the%20institutions%20waking%20up%20to%20their%20responsibilities.%20and%20I%20sincerely%20hope%20the%20court%20intervenes%20and%20takes%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20journalists%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20academics%2C%20students%20have%20also%20been%20picked%20up%20and%20thrown%20into%20prison.%20And%20hate%20speakers%20are%20simply%20let%20off%20the%20hook%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20look%20at%20the%20hate%20economy%20all%20the%20time.%20We%20are%20filing%20petition%20after%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20almost%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20like%20on%20the%20dharam%20sansad%20etc%2C%20but%20very%20little%20has%20come%20out%20of%20it.%20Why%20should%20hate%20speeches%20have%20to%20go%20to%20court%3F%20The%20process%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20wherever%20a%20hate%20speech%20is%20made%2C%20the%20local%20administration%20should%20move%20in%2C%20file%20an%20FIR%2C%20investigate%20the%20case%2C%20and%20people%20punished.%20All%20these%20hate%20speeches%20are%20made%20mostly%20in%20areas%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20just%20got%20a%20couple%20of%20orders%20from%20Justice%20KM%20Joseph%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20retired%20now.%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20is%20looking%20at%20matters%20today%2C%20he%20has%20taken%20some%20effective%20steps%2C%20hope%20it%20works%20out.%20Justice%20Khanna%20is%20also%20in%20line%20to%20be%20the%20next%20chief%20justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20pick%20up%20journalists%2C%20activists%2C%20academics%2C%20students%2C%20and%20members%20of%20the%20minority%20communities%2C%20those%20who%20speak%20against%20the%20government%20and%20voice%20dissent.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20of%20course%20without%20any%20basis%2C%20but%20they%20foist%20cases%20on%20them%2C%20from%20sedition%20to%20causing%20enmity%20etc%20under%20sections%20153%20A%2C%20298%20A%20of%20the%20IPC.%20Cases%20are%20lodged%20against%20people%20based%20on%20all%20kinds%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%20which%20have%20no%20basis%20at%20all%2C%20but%20court%20procedures%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20safeguards%20then%2C%20to%20ensure%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20poll%20before%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20hope%20is%20the%20court.%20We%20should%20go%20back%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20we%20will%20file%20a%20comprehensive%20petition%20for%20electoral%20reform%20to%20make%20the%20process%20of%20election%20fair%2C%20which%20will%20of%20course%2C%20include%20the%20insistence%20on%20a%20totaliser.%20I%20think%20the%20court%20and%20political%20parties%20must%20rule%20in%20favour%20of%20totalisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20also%20see%20how%20they%20manipulate%20the%20election%20results%2C%20the%20deletion%20of%20people%20on%20the%20electoral%20roll%2C%20deletion%20of%20families%20or%20particular%20communities.%20Or%2C%20how%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20police%20forces%20disallow%20people%20to%20go%20out%20and%20vote%2C%20the%20EVMs%2C%20the%20paper%20trail%2C%20etc.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20wake%20up%20the%20nation%20on%20all%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696413614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F16133352%2Fkapil-sibal-congress.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-kapil-sibal-thinks-electoral-reforms-evm-totalisers-are-necessities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFor%20electoral%20fairness%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20political%20parties%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20manipulate%20results%2C%20and%20a%20totaliser%20would%20have%20ensured%20that%20political%20parties%20have%20no%20access%20to%20find%20out%20how%20citizens%20have%20voted%20and%20for%20which%20party%20in%20any%20particular%20booth.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-kapil-sibal-thinks-electoral-reforms-evm-totalisers-are-necessities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20big%20revelations%20from%20the%20new%20Beckham%20Netflix%20documentary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696413000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-victoria-adams-victoria-beckham_6308389.jpg%3F20231004103413%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdavid-beckham-netflix-documentary-five-big-revelations-from-alleged-rebecca-loos-affair-to-world-cup-pain-12976472%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20documentary%20delves%20into%20the%20life%20of%20David%20B