sclick%20in%20Official%20Statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04143738%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20independent%20news%20website%2C%20editors%2C%20journalists%2C%20part-time%20employees%20and%20contributors%20of%20which%20were%20targeted%20and%20subjected%20to%20raids%2C%20device%20seizures%2C%20questioning%20and%20arrests%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20has%20released%20a%20statement%20noting%20they%20are%20still%20in%20the%20dark%20over%20the%20case%20which%20led%20to%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20action%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20statement%2C%20released%20a%20day%20after%20the%20website%E2%80%99s%20director%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20one%20Amit%20Chakraborty%20were%20arrested%2C%20said%20that%20Newsclick%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20provided%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20first%20information%20report%20against%20it%20or%20%E2%80%9Cinformed%20about%20the%20exact%20particulars%20of%20the%20offences%20with%20which%20we%20have%20been%20charged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20gather%20is%20that%20Newsclick%20stands%20accused%20of%20offences%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20for%20purportedly%20carrying%20Chinese%20propaganda%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20condemn%20these%20actions%20of%20a%20Government%20that%20refuses%20to%20respect%20journalistic%20independence%2C%20and%20treats%20criticism%20as%20sedition%20or%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20action%20is%20in%20connection%20with%20FIR%20number%20224%2F2023%2C%20which%20invokes%20sections%20of%20the%20draconian%20UAPA.%C2%A0The%20FIR%2C%20it%20is%20believed%2C%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20August%20which%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%5C%22%3E%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20claim%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20notes%20that%20all%20journalistic%20content%20ever%20published%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20website%20is%20available%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20can%20be%20seen%20by%20anyone%20and%20that%2C%20notably%2C%20police%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20focus%20on%20this%20%E2%80%98Chinese%20propaganda%E2%80%99%20angle%20during%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Special%20Cell%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20not%20referred%20to%20a%20single%20article%20or%20video%20that%20they%20consider%20to%20be%20Chinese%20propaganda.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-journos-questioned-delhi-riots-farmers-protest-covid-crisis%5C%22%3Eline%20of%20questioning%20adopted%20by%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20regarding%20reportage%20on%20the%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20the%20farmers%20protests%20etc.%2C%20all%20demonstrate%20the%20motivated%20and%20malicious%20intent%20behind%20the%20present%20proceedings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20on%20October%203%20began%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20involved%20over%2040%20locations%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai.%20In%20total%2C%2037%20men%20and%20nine%20women%20were%20raided%20and%20questioned%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDevices%20belonging%20to%20staffers%20old%20and%20new%20were%20seized%20by%20police.%20Some%20journalists%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Cell%20at%20Lodhi%20Road%20for%20questioning%20%E2%80%93%20which%20continued%20until%20late%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENewsclick%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20no%20adherence%20to%20due%20process%20when%20the%20devices%20were%20seized%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElectronic%20devices%20were%20seized%20from%20the%20Newsclick%20premises%20and%20homes%20of%20employees%2C%20without%20any%20adherence%20to%20due%20process%20such%20as%20the%20provision%20of%20seizure%20memos%2C%20hash%20values%20of%20the%20seized%20data%2C%20or%20even%20copies%20of%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20said%20that%20its%20office%20has%20also%20been%20sealed%2C%20in%20what%20it%20called%20was%20a%20blatant%20attempt%20at%20preventing%20them%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20continuing%20%5Btheir%5D%20reporting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20noted%20that%20the%20website%20has%20been%20targeted%20before%20but%20that%20little%20headway%20was%20made%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20even%20though%20seizures%20happened%20then%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20targeted%20by%20a%20series%20of%20actions%20by%20various%20agencies%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20since%202021.%20Its%20offices%20and%20residences%20of%20officials%20have%20been%20raided%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20devices%2C%20laptops%2C%20gadgets%2C%20phones%2C%20etc.%20have%20been%20seized%20in%20the%20past.%20All%20emails%20and%20communications%20have%20been%20analysed%20under%20the%20microscope.%20All%20bank%20statements%2C%20invoices%2C%20expenses%20incurred%2C%20sources%20of%20funds%20received%20by%20Newsclick%20in%20the%20last%20several%20years%20have%20been%20scrutinised%20by%20different%20agencies%20of%20the%20Government%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Various%20directors%20and%20other%20related%20persons%20have%20spent%20countless%20hours%20on%20several%20occasions%20being%20interrogated%20by%20these%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20observes%20that%20in%20spite%20of%20such%20action%2C%20in%20the%20last%20two%20plus%20years%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20accusing%20Newsclick%20of%20money%20laundering.%E2%80%9D%20Nor%20has%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20been%20able%20to%20file%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20Newsclick%20for%20offences%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20or%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20been%20able%20to%20defend%20its%20actions%20before%20the%20courts%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20several%20months%2C%20Mr.%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20has%20not%20even%20been%20called%20in%20for%20questioning%20by%20any%20of%20these%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENewsclick%20has%20called%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%20and%20bogus.%E2%80%9D%20Notably%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmanolo_realengo%2Fstatus%2F1709334268332110058%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DZJCJhEAnpz0jFlEdwtO2BQ%5C%22%3Eprotests%20outside%20the%20NYT%E2%80%99s%20offices%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20over%20the%20article%20and%20its%20repercussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20a%20Government%20that%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20substantiate%20any%20charges%20against%20Newsclick%20despite%20being%20in%20possession%20of%20all%20its%20information%2C%20documentation%20and%20communications%2C%20needed%20a%20motivated%20and%20bogus%20article%20published%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20to%20invoke%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20and%20attempt%20to%20shut%20down%20and%20stifle%20independent%20and%20fearless%20voices%20that%20portray%20the%20story%20of%20the%20real%20India%20%E2%80%93%20of%20peasants%2C%20of%20labourers%2C%20of%20farmers%2C%20and%20other%20oft-ignored%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20statement%2C%20Newsclick%20has%20said%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20state%20for%20the%20record%2C%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%20Newsclick%20is%20an%20independent%20news%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2.%20Our%20journalistic%20content%20is%20based%20on%20highest%20standards%20of%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3.%20Newsclick%20does%20not%20publish%20any%20news%20or%20information%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20any%20Chinese%20entity%20or%20authority%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20Newsclick%20does%20not%20propagate%20Chinese%20propaganda%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E5.%20Newsclick%20does%20not%20take%20directions%20from%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20regarding%20the%20content%20published%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6.%20All%20funding%20received%20by%20Newsclick%20has%20been%20through%20the%20appropriate%20banking%20channels%20and%20have%20been%20reported%20to%20the%20relevant%20authorities%20as%20required%20by%20law%2C%20as%20substantiated%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20in%20proceedings%20before%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20ends%20with%20the%20words%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20Courts%20and%20the%20judicial%20process.%20We%20will%20fight%20for%20our%20journalistic%20freedom%20and%20our%20lives%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696411803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04143738%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-fir-china-delhi-police-attack-on-media%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'We%20strongly%20condemn%20these%20actions%20of%20a%20Government%20that%20refuses%20to%20respect%20journalistic%20independence%2C%20and%20treats%20criticism%20as%20sedition%20or%20'anti-national'%20propaganda.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-fir-china-delhi-police-attack-on-media%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Torrent%20files%20urgent%20plea%20in%20SC%20against%20Hinduja%20plan%20for%20Reliance%20Capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696410037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F26%2Ffull%2F1679825184-8358.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-files-urgent-plea-in-sc-against-hinduja-plan-for-reliance-capital-123100400579_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Company%20says%20insolvency%20tribunal%20approved%20plan%20when%20appeals%20against%20it%20are%20pending%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-files-urgent-plea-in-sc-against-hinduja-plan-for-reliance-capital-123100400579_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-files-urgent-plea-in-sc-against-hinduja-plan-for-reliance-capital-123100400579_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-files-urgent-plea-in-sc-against-hinduja-plan-for-reliance-capital-123100400579_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Misogyny%20on%20the%20Carnatic%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04141728%2FThe-Wire-29.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201926%2C%20Bangalore%20Nagarathnamma%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20annual%20tribute%20to%20Saint%20Thyagaraja%20%E2%80%93%20because%20she%20was%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20constructing%20his%20temple%20at%20her%20personal%20expense.%20It%20was%201941%20before%20men%20and%20women%20could%20perform%20together%20at%20the%20Thiruvaiyaru%20Thyagaraja%20Aradhana.%20Now%20the%20armed%20forces%20have%20men%20and%20women%2C%20co-educational%20schools%20are%20the%20norm%2C%20workplaces%20are%20gender-neutral%2C%20and%20unisex%20restrooms%20are%20increasingly%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20has%20the%20gender%20dynamic%20evolved%20on%20the%20Carnatic%20stage%20during%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20is%20undoubtedly%20better%20now%2C%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20we%20have%20to%20compare%20our%20state%20with%20women%20of%20over%2050%20years%20ago%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20men%20of%20today%20%E2%80%93%20consoling%20ourselves%20that%20things%20are%20not%20too%20bad%20after%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20vocalist%20Nisha%20Rajagopalan.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20understood%2C%20and%20accepted%20by%20all%2C%20that%20the%20senior-most%20generation%20of%20currently%20performing%20artistes%20does%20not%20play%20with%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20clarifies.%20Vocalist%20Sangeetha%20Sivakumar%20says%20categorically%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20woman%20who%20has%20not%20faced%20this%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fmadras-music-season%5C%22%3EMadras%20Music%20Season%2C%20a%20Festival%20of%20Elite%20Castes%20Where%20Non-Brahmins%20Are%20Nearly%20Invisible%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20rarely%20registers%20this%20fact%20though%2C%20since%20they%20do%20see%20some%20men%20and%20women%20performing%20together%20at%20concerts%2C%20and%20statistics%2C%20such%20as%20the%20publicly%20available%20list%20of%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi%20awardees%2C%20show%20significant%20progress.%20Arguably%20the%20most%20coveted%20title%20in%20Carnatic%20Music%2C%20the%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi%20is%20awarded%20annually%20by%20The%20Music%20Academy%20in%20Chennai.%20Between%202010%20and%202023%2C%20eight%20of%2016%20(50%25)%20awardees%20were%20female%20versus%20just%20nine%20out%20of%2080%20(11.25%25)%20in%20the%20previous%20hundred%20years%2C%20between%201929-2009.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fmadras-music_facebook-1024x680-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fmadras-music_facebook-1024x680-1.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fmadras-music_facebook-1024x680-1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fmadras-music_facebook-1024x680-1-768x510.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-86601%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20performance%20at%20a%20previous%20Madras%20Music%20Season.%20Credit%3A%20Facebook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20happens%20unbeknownst%20to%20the%20audience%20is%20disheartening.%20Sangeet%20Natak%20Akademi%20Puraskar%20awardee%2C%20and%20veteran%20ghatam%20player%2C%20Sukanya%20Ramgopal%20was%20turned%20back%20at%20a%20concert%20venue%20from%20performing%20because%20the%20mridangist%20(now%20a%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi)%20refused%20to%20play%20with%20a%20woman.%20An%20accompanying%20violinist%20was%20told%20that%20the%20mridangist%20objected%20to%20women%20on%20stage%20%E2%80%93%20she%20stepped%20down.%20Mridangist%20Rajna%20Swaminathan%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi%20Umayalpuram%20K.%20Sivaraman%2C%20was%20questioned%20on%20her%20competency%20by%20the%20male%20vocalist%20she%20was%20to%20accompany%20%E2%80%93%20who%20then%20recused%20himself.%20A%20male%20violinist%20about%20to%20play%20a%20solo%20refused%20to%20have%20a%20female%20tambura%20player%20on%20stage%20%E2%80%93%20without%20demur%2C%20the%20organiser%20(a%20female)%20sent%20the%20already-arrived%20lady%20strummer%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20system%20of%20rewarding%20misogynistic%20musicians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20themselves%20rarely%20discuss%20this%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20openly.%20Sukanya%20Ramgopal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20be%20ostracised%20from%20the%20performing%20scene%20if%20they%20speak%20out.%E2%80%9D%20The%20community%20is%20small%20and%20the%20misogynists%E2%80%99%20networks%20run%20wide%20and%20deep.%20Fear%20of%20backlash%20is%20high%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20for%20younger%20musicians.%20Musician%20activist%20T.M.%20Krishna%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20are%20seniors%20who%20have%20nothing%20left%20to%20achieve%20tight-lipped%20about%20this%2C%20but%20they%20also%20encourage%20other%20musicians%20to%20stay%20mum%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%20Mridangist%20composer%20K.%20Arun%20Prakash%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20society%20as%20a%20whole%20does%20not%20decry%20this%20practice%2C%20individual%20ladies%20cannot%20point%20it%20out.%20Those%20who%20do%20will%20be%20avoided.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20system%2C%20worryingly%2C%20appears%20to%20reward%20misogynistic%20musicians%2C%20encouraging%20future%20generations%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20path.%20Among%20the%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi%20awardees%2C%20for%20example%2C%20only%20two%20male%20vocalists%2C%20Dr.%20S.%20Ramanathan%20and%20M.%20Balamuralikrishna%2C%20appear%20to%20have%20performed%20with%20women%20throughout.%20Otherwise%2C%20most%20of%20the%20other%20recipients%20(vocalists%20and%20instrumentalists)%20are%20either%20artistes%20who%20have%20never%20shared%20the%20stage%20with%20women%2C%20or%20those%20who%20initially%20did%20so%20and%20then%20stopped%2C%20or%20those%20who%20included%20women%20only%20after%20receiving%20all%20major%20awards.%20With%20a%20long%20history%20of%20the%20name%20and%20fame%20of%20misogynists%20rivalling%20that%20of%20egalitarian%20musicians%2C%20gender%20segregation%20has%20earned%20legitimacy%2C%20appearing%20necessary%20to%20achieve%20pinnacles%20of%20glory%20%E2%80%93%20some%20musicians%20as%20young%20as%20in%20their%2030s%20have%20boycotted%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThickly%20shrouded%20in%20tradition%2C%20Carnatic%20music%20lays%20heavy%20emphasis%20on%20age%20and%20longevity%20in%20the%20field%2C%20automatically%20legitimising%20seniors%E2%80%99%20actions%2C%20even%20those%20that%20are%20obviously%20wrong.%20The%20segregationist%20actions%20of%20senior%20and%20senior-citizen%20musicians%2C%20deified%20for%20their%20on-stage%20artistry%2C%20resulting%20in%20women%20being%20seen%20as%20dispensable%20and%20substitutable%2C%20giving%20them%20negligible%20bargaining%20power%20for%20prime%20slots%2C%20co-artistes%20or%20remuneration.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20happened%20in%20any%20other%20sphere%20of%20life%2C%20the%20office%2C%20for%20example%2C%20everyone%20would%20be%20up%20in%20arms%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20T.M.%20Krishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerformers%20depend%20on%20public%20perception.%20Comments%20like%20%E2%80%98This%20new%20musician%20MUST%20be%20good%20because%20senior%20XYZ%20is%20performing%20alongside%E2%80%99%20are%20common.%20Between%20foisted%20competence%20on%20the%20younger%20artiste%20and%20the%20senior%E2%80%99s%20own%20fan%20following%2C%20audiences%20automatically%20mushroom%2C%20propelling%20the%20aspiring%20artiste%E2%80%99s%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcarnatic-music-plagiarism-tradition%5C%22%3EThose%20Who%20Talk%20of%20Plagiarism%20in%20Carnatic%20Music%20Know%20Not%20About%20the%20Tradition%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENisha%20Rajagopalan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20upcoming%20male%20artistes%20perform%20with%20these%20senior%20artistes%20and%20get%20a%20leg%20up%20for%20advancement%20to%20%E2%80%98main%20concert%20slots%E2%80%99%2C%20whereas%20most%20women%20spend%20years%20and%20years%20struggling%20to%20make%20their%20way%20up%20the%20ladder.%E2%80%9D%20T.M.%20Krishna%20confirms%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20and%20other%20male%20artistes%20indeed%20got%2Fget%20headstarts%20in%20this%20manner.%20Sangeetha%20Sivakumar%2C%20also%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20has%20seen%20this%20play%20out%20before%20her%20eyes.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CSince%20women%20do%20not%20receive%20this%20opportunity%2C%20it%20begins%20a%20gap%20between%20otherwise%20equal%20musicians%20that%20keeps%20widening%20with%20time%2C%20setting%20women%20up%20for%20permanent%20second-class%20status.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeniors%20frequently%20say%20they%20perform%20alongside%20%E2%80%98younger%20musicians%E2%80%99%20to%20encourage%20them%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20that%20is%20true%20or%20a%20shrewd%20strategy%20to%20ensure%20ongoing%20relevance%20in%20a%20highly%20competitive%20artform%20is%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20guess.%20What%20is%20a%20fact%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98encouragement%E2%80%99%20is%20reserved%20only%20for%20men.%20Vocalist%2C%20vainika%20and%20scholar%2C%20Dr.%20S.%20Sowmya%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20male%20child%20sings%2C%20they%20will%20play%2C%20but%20however%20seasoned%20a%20female%20artiste%2C%20they%20will%20not.%20It%20is%20absolute%20chauvinism%20and%20still%20happens.%E2%80%9D%20Musician%20and%20scholar%20R.K.%20Shriramkumar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20sad%20that%20people%20have%20such%20views%20%E2%80%93%20many%20meritorious%20women%20do%20not%20get%20the%20recognition%20they%20deserve%20as%20a%20result.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20automatic%20assumption%20that%20veteran%20stalwarts%20perform%20alongside%20the%20most%20competent%20musicians%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20of%20the%20deep-rooted%20gender%20bias%2C%20results%20in%20male%20performers%20and%20%E2%80%98male%20music%E2%80%99%20being%20considered%20superior.%20The%20corollary%20is%20reduced%20expectations%20from%20women.%20Brindha%20Manickavasakan%20recollects%20one%20concert%20vividly.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20sung%20some%20%3Cem%3Ekanakku%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mathematical%20permutations%20and%20combinations%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekalpanaswaras%3C%2Fem%3E).%20After%20the%20concert%2C%20a%20few%20people%20came%20up%20and%20said%20all%20I%20was%20expected%20to%20do%20was%20to%20sing%20in%20tune%20%E2%80%93%20there%20were%20male%20musicians%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Ekanakku%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Such%20ingrained%20perceptions%20probably%20also%20explain%20why%20female%20musicians%20are%20rarely%20chosen%20to%20showcase%20%3Cem%3Earangetram%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stage%20debut)%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20also%20means%20that%20if%20male%20musicians%20perform%20with%20women%2C%20they%20can%20call%20attention%20to%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98socially%20conscious%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20another%20musician.%20When%20vocalist%20Aishwarya%20Vidhya%20Raghunath%20enquired%20about%20a%20performing%20opportunity%2C%20the%20organiser%20said%20he%20had%20numerous%20male%20alternatives%20available%20(naming%20several%20contemporaries).%20Whether%20headliner%20or%20accompanying%20artiste%2C%20every%20woman%20is%20affected.%20Sukanya%20Ramgopal%20thinks%20the%20situation%20has%20worsened%20in%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20%E2%80%9CMore%20musicians%20have%20pre-set%20teams%2C%20leading%20to%20fewer%20musicians%20that%20they%20collaborate%20with.%20Females%20are%20the%20first%20casualty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20careers%2C%20musicians%20perform%20with%20a%20large%20set%20of%20co-artistes%2C%20often%20including%20women.%20With%20increased%20fame%2C%20they%20become%20more%20specific.%20That%20is%20understandable%20as%20certain%20styles%20and%20personalities%20just%20jell%20better.%20However%2C%20some%20are%20highly%20restrictive%2C%20such%20as%20the%20vocalist%20who%20performs%20with%20only%20one%20particular%20violinist%20and%20one%20particular%20mridangist%20and%20another%20violinist%20who%20plays%20with%20only%20one%20vocalist.%20Nor%20is%20this%20confined%20to%20men%20and%2For%20senior%20citizen%20musicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20female%20accompanying%20violinists%20of%20the%20highest%20skill%20levels%20is%20in%20the%20single%20digits%20and%20even%20lesser%20with%20percussionists.%C2%A0Sangeetha%20Sivakumar%20finds%20this%20unsurprising%2C%20given%20the%20lack%20of%20satisfying%20opportunities%20and%20multiple%20barriers%20for%20female%20accompanying%20musicians.%20%C2%A0Of%20the%20bare%20handful%20of%20such%20violinists%2C%20one%20performs%20only%20with%20a%20few%20female%20headliners%20and%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20males.%20Another%20plays%20only%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20exclusively%20male%20headliners.%20Such%20uber-choosiness%20further%20exacerbates%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20women%20prefer%20performing%20with%20men.%20Sangeetha%20Sivakumar%20opines%2C%20%E2%80%9CMale%20or%20female%2C%20all%20artistes%20are%20trying%20to%20gain%20standing%20and%20advance%20in%20the%20field%20and%20will%20collaborate%20with%20whomever%20will%20most%20facilitate%20that.%20Since%20the%20entire%20system%20is%20weighted%20towards%20men%2C%20it%20becomes%20natural%20for%20many%20to%20prefer%20performing%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%20T.M.%20Krishna%20agrees%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20in%20any%20other%20field%2C%20people%20imitate%20those%20in%20positions%20of%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESegregationist%20artistes%20boycott%20female%20performers%20with%20impunity%20but%20continue%20to%20be%20kept%20on%20pedestals%20and%20recognised%20at%20the%20highest%20levels.%20This%20reveals%20how%20entrenched%20sexism%20is.%20Krishna%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20happened%20in%20any%20other%20sphere%20of%20life%2C%20the%20office%2C%20for%20example%2C%20everyone%20would%20be%20up%20in%20arms.%20But%20Carnatic%20music%20is%20decades%20behind.%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20Prakash%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COrganisations%20are%20hand-in-hand.%20If%20a%20male%20artiste%20says%20no%20to%20women%2C%20no%20questions%20are%20asked.%20He%20is%20fixed%20with%20other%20male%20artistes%20automatically.%20His%20prestige%20would%20even%20go%20up.%E2%80%9D%20Some%20segregationists%20told%20Arun%20Prakash%20that%20if%20he%20became%20male-only%2C%20they%20would%20take%20him%20for%20their%20concerts%20while%20others%20asked%20why%20he%20demeaned%20himself%20accompanying%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMisogynist%20musicians%E2%80%99%20reasons%20for%20boycotting%20women%20performers%20are%20nebulous%20and%20contradictory.%20%C2%A0Violinists%20cite%20women%E2%80%99s%20higher%20pitches%20as%20detrimental%20to%20the%20longevity%20of%20their%20playing%20careers.%20Yet%2C%20they%20do%20not%20accompany%20women%20performing%20at%20lower%20%E2%80%98male%E2%80%99%20pitches%20whilst%20accompanying%20male%20solo%20instrumentalists%20playing%20at%20%E2%80%98female%E2%80%99%20high%20pitches.%20Mridangists%20say%20they%20cannot%20play%20with%20abandon%20due%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98lighter%E2%80%99%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Sangeetha%20Sivakumar%20says%2C%20there%20are%20men%20with%20lighter%20voices%20too%20just%20as%20there%20are%20women%20with%20heavier%20ones.%20Some%20perform%20with%20female%20family%20members%20or%20alongside%20sibling%20duos%20where%20one%20sibling%20is%20male.%20Seeking%20to%20avoid%20women%E2%80%99s%20interfering%20husbands%20has%20been%20mentioned%20as%20an%20issue%20%E2%80%93%20Dr.%20Sowmya%20remarks%20that%20they%20never%20performed%20with%20single%20women%20either.%20Others%20cite%20old%20beliefs%20surrounding%20menstruating%20women%20%E2%80%93%20however%2C%20they%20performed%20earlier%20with%20younger%20women%20and%20then%20later%20stopped%2C%20not%20playing%20even%20with%20post-menopausal%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ET.M.%20Krishna%20says%20these%20are%20all%20mere%20red%20herrings.%20%E2%80%9CMen%20fear%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20noticed%20if%20a%20woman%20is%20on%20stage%20with%20them.%20They%20believe%20all%20the%20attention%20will%20be%20on%20the%20woman%20since%20she%20is%20sexualised%20%E2%80%93%20objectified.%E2%80%9D%20The%20hypocrisy%20of%20%E2%80%98exalted%E2%80%99%20segregationist%20musicians%20extolling%20the%20female%20divine%2C%20being%20feminist%20in%20words%20but%20entirely%20chauvinistic%20in%20action%2C%20is%20an%20especially%20despicable%20aspect%20of%20Carnatic%20music%2C%20particularly%20in%20its%20mecca%20of%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20female%20musicians%20spoken%20to%2C%20in%20one%20voice%2C%20acknowledged%20their%20satisfaction%20with%20those%20artistes%20who%20do%20collaborate%20with%20them%20gender%20notwithstanding.%20One%20has%20to%20wonder%20though%2C%20whether%20some%2C%20or%20all%2C%20will%20eventually%20boycott%20women%20%E2%80%93%20as%20many%20of%20their%20predecessors%20have.%20Can%20women%20call%20out%20the%20discrimination%20unitedly%3F%20Can%20the%20men%20show%20their%20support%20by%20performing%20only%20with%20co-artistes%20who%20do%20not%20gender%20discriminate%3F%20Can%20corporate%20sponsors%20set%20gender%20equity%20guidelines%20for%20what%20they%20fund%3F%20Can%20organisations%20recognise%20and%20back%20artistes%20who%20have%2C%20sans%20fuss%20and%20fanfare%2C%20practiced%20gender%20equality%3F%20Most%20importantly%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20most%20effectively%2C%20can%20rasikas%20observe%20for%20such%20facets%20and%20openly%20question%20artistes%20and%20organisers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Navaratri%20Mandapam%20Music%20Festival%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20shows%20organisational%20change%20is%20possible.%20Women%20were%20barred%20from%20performing%20at%2C%20or%20attending%2C%20this%20festival%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20centuries%20of%20history.%20In%202006%2C%20Aswati%20Tirunal%20Rama%20Varma%2C%20a%20scion%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20of%20Travancore%2C%20opened%20up%20the%20festival%20to%20women.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20at%20least%20one%20female%20performer%20every%20year%20and%20women%20are%20welcome%20to%20attend%20all%20the%20concerts.%20%E2%80%9CNavaratri%20is%20a%20festival%20celebrating%20the%20female%20Goddess%3B%20it%20was%20illogical%20to%20disallow%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rama%20Varma%20to%20this%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20however%2C%20what%20rather%20damningly%20holds%20in%20Carnatic%20Music%20is%20an%20adaptation%20of%20George%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20caustic%20line%20from%3Cem%3E%20Animal%20Farm%3C%2Fem%3E.%20All%20musicians%20are%20equal%20but%20males%20are%20more%20equal%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELakshmi%20Anand%20is%20a%20Kalpalata%20Fellow%20for%20Classical%20Music%20Writings%20for%202022%20and%202023.%20She%20is%20an%20associate%20editor%20on%20the%20Editorial%20Board%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EIndian%20Journal%20of%20Performing%20Arts%20Education%20and%20Research%2C%20%3Cem%3Epublished%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Dr.%20J.%20Jayalalithaa%20Music%20and%20Fine%20Arts%20University.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696410030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04141728%2FThe-Wire-29.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fmisogyny-on-the-carnatic-stage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Segregationist%20artistes%20boycott%20female%20performers%20with%20impunity%20but%20continue%20to%20be%20kept%20on%20pedestals%20and%20recognised%20at%20the%20highest%20levels.%20This%20reveals%20how%20entrenched%20sexism%20is.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fmisogyny-on-the-carnatic-stage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HDFC%20Bank%20disburses%20Rs%2048k%20crore