%20interests%20shifted%20to%20rural%20development%2C%20social%2C%20and%20environmental%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhulika%2C%20who%20pursued%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20telecommunications%20from%20the%20US%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20our%20marriage%2C%20we%20have%20lived%20in%20different%20cities%20and%20countries%20as%20well.%20But%20we%20had%20decided%20to%20settle%20in%20Rajasthan%20while%20we%20were%20still%20in%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20settling%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Dungarpur%20in%20South%20Rajasthan%2C%20they%20lived%20in%20several%20cities%20like%20Anantpur%2C%20Udaipur%2C%20Chittorgarh%2C%20Bhilwara%2C%20and%20a%20few%20villages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20lived%20in%20state%20capitals%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20quiet%20place%20without%20traffic%20noise.%20We%20discovered%20this%20town%20to%20be%20peaceful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashis%2C%20who%20currently%20heads%20an%20NGO%20Sambhaav%20Trust%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20couple%20purchased%20the%20land%20and%20began%20researching%20ways%20to%20create%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244161%2Fthese-10-eco-friendly-homes-will-inspire-you-to-live-sustainably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20friendly%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20sustainable%20house.%20They%20spent%2010%20months%20on%20this%20research%2C%20during%20which%20they%20consulted%20with%20several%20architects%20and%20studied%20houses%20as%20old%20as%20150%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20841px)%20100vw%2C%20841px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%201999%2C%20Ashish%20and%20Madhulika%20met%20while%20studying%20at%20BITS%20Pilani.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22841%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331352%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%201999%2C%20Ashis%20and%20Madhulika%20met%20while%20studying%20at%20BITS%20Pilani.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20traditional%20materials%20used%20by%20the%20local%20people.%20We%20discovered%20that%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20old%20houses%2C%20palaces%2C%20and%20mansions%20were%20built%20with%20stone%20and%20lime.%20These%20structures%2C%20despite%20not%20using%20cement%20and%20steel%2C%20have%20endured%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20outperformed%20RCC-built%20homes%2C%20which%20often%20deteriorate%20in%20just%20a%20few%20decades%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20Ashis%20and%20Madhulika%20employed%20a%20traditional%20roof%20construction%20method.%20They%20mixed%20lime%2C%20jaggery%2C%20fenugreek%2C%20and%20ropes%20for%20this%20purpose.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20the%20roof%20cool%20and%20waterproof%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConstructed%20in%20an%20area%20of%203%2C200%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20two-storey%20house%20features%20two%20covered%20verandahs%2C%20a%20dining%20area%2C%20an%20open%20verandah%2C%20three%20bedrooms%20with%20two%20attached%20washrooms%20and%20one%