ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-2-1696338727-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-2-1696338727-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331411%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDeepak%20says%20that%20it%20was%20only%20because%20of%20Kapurchand%20Jain%20that%20they%20earned%20fame%20worldwide.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20akhara%20to%20the%20royal%20kitchen%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20starting%20the%20shop%2C%20Parmanand%20Jain%20worked%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhansama%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cook)%20in%20the%20royal%20kitchen.%20Deepak%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20be%20called%20to%20make%20sweets%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330673%2Fgi-tagged-mithai-sweets-of-india-dharwad-peda-bebinca-khaje-moa-mihidana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20occasions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20such%20a%20perfect%20cook%20that%20he%20earned%20the%20title%20of%20%3Cem%3EBhakt%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20kind%20of%20honorific%20at%20that%20time)%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20was%20no%20less%20than%20any%20award.%20Alongside%20this%20work%2C%20he%20used%20to%20sell%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20%3Cem%3Emisri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(rock%20sugar)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emawa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(dried%20whole%20milk).%20At%20that%20time%2C%20these%20sweets%20were%20the%20trend%20and%20were%20largely%20in%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20once%20when%20Parmanand%20Jain%20was%20slow-boiling%20the%20milk%2C%20he%20accidentally%20reduced%20it%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20he%20invited%20his%20wrestler%20friends%20to%20taste%20the%20sweet%2C%20they%20were%20in%20awe.%20Thereafter%2C%20Parmanand%20Jain%20s