er%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311261%2Fmumbai-shilpa-mehta-jain-affected-by-polio-becomes-ca-starts-scholarship-for-disabled-people%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eability%20to%20walk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20his%20parents%20took%20him%20to%20numerous%20hospitals%20and%20tried%20everything%20but%20the%20damage%20was%20irreversible.%20It%20was%20these%20hospital%20visits%20that%20motivated%20Shravan%20to%20pursue%20medicine%20and%20raise%20awareness%20of%20polio%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20chasing%20this%20dream%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disqualified%20from%20appearing%20for%20the%20Pre-Medical%20Test%20(PMT)%20due%20to%20the%2080%20percent%20disability%20in%20my%20lower%20limbs.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20the%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court.%20Through%20their%20intervention%2C%20I%20enrolled%20for%20MBBS.%20After%20five%20years%20of%20devotion%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20I%20became%20a%20doctor!%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2045-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20medical%20officer%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan%20and%20worked%20to%20raise%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F165487%2Findia-polio-vaccination-workers-method-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawareness%20about%20polio%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20tell%20my%20story%20to%20parents%20who%20are%20still%20afraid%20of%20vaccines%2C%20even%20decades%20after%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20campaign.%20We%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20to%20fight%20this%20fear%2C%20and%20I%20am%20going%20to%20do%20my%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxzC3Wpo7JD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no