ur%20first%20collection%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.econock.com%2Fpages%2Fsophisticated-survivor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESophisticated%20Survivor%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20Econock%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ribhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20source%20material%20Econock%20employs%20is%20leather%20scraps%20which%20are%20oddly%20shaped%20and%20sized.%20They%20are%20mostly%20remains%20and%20cut-outs%20of%20larger%20leather%20skins.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Nora%20Tote%20Bag%20from%20our%20Sophisticated%20Survivor%20collection.%20The%20base%20is%20made%20out%20of%20waste%20leather.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20two%20halves%20on%20the%20surface%20are%20created%20from%20a%20single%20sheet%20of%20leather%20with%20the%20positive%20part%20placed%20on%20the%20upper%20panel%20and%20the%20remaining%20waste%20utilised%20in%20the%20bottom%20sections%20so%20that%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263620%2Ffarmse-farms-on-wheels-organic-zero-waste-store-ahmedabad-organic-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20wastage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ribhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20the%20fashion%20industry%20needs%20to%20be%20mindful%20while%20creating%20new%20products%20and%20designs%20and%20be%20conscious%20of%20the%20wastage%20that%20is%20generated.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20world%20where%20high%20fashion%20is%20synonymous%20with%20sustainability%2C%20where%20each%20piece%20is%20thoughtfully%20crafted%20to%20minimise%20waste%20and%20be%20environmentally%20conscious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb